detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on August 5.

detail_zh: 患者為私家醫生，會到不同院舍看診，8 月 5 日出現症狀，潛服期間曾到安泰邨服務設施大樓 5 樓及 6 樓的的聖雅各福群會復康服務忻明居及悅明居看診。7 月 22 日曾到沙田佳景護老院、沙田柔濟安老院、何文田永安護老中心及大埔康和護老中心。7 月 24 日則到過葵涌松濤護老中心、深水埗樂順護老院、旺角木蘭護老院及新填地街唯愛護老院。
detail_en: The patient is a private practitioner offering elderly home visits, and he developed symptoms on August 5. During the incubation period, he visited St. James’ Settlement Rehabilitation Services Cheerful Residence and Blissful Residence on 5/F and 6/F, On Tai Estate Ancillary Facilities Block. On July 22, he visited Kai King Home of Aged, Shatin; Yau Chai Home of Aged, Shatin; Wing On Home for the Aged, Homantin; and Cornwall Elderly's Home, Tai Po. On July 24, he visited Chung Tao Elderly Centre, Kwai Chung; Loc Shun Elderly Home, Sham Shui Po; Mu Lan Home for the Aged, Mong Kok; and Elderly Home of Love, Reclamation Street.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者有長期病患，7 月 24 日出現症狀，8 月 3 日因發燒經急症室入住監察病房，同日接受病毒測試，其鼻咽抽取液及咽喉拭子樣本化驗結果為陰性，由於情況不穩定，8 月 4 日轉到深切治療部病房。因患者有喉嚨痛及腹瀉症狀，8 月 5 日被安排轉到監察病房再次作病毒化驗，當時結果為陰性，8 月 6 日因外科問題轉到普通外科病房繼續治療。患者由 8 月 6 日開始發燒，基於臨床決定，8 月 8 日被安排轉到監察病房並再次進行病毒化驗，最終化驗結果為陽性，隨即轉到隔離病房治療。
detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions and developed symptoms on July 24. He was admitted to an observation ward through A&E upon developing fever on August 3, and his nasal and throat swaps tested negative on that day. He was transferred to intensive care unit due to unstable conditions on August 4, and then observation ward for re-test on August 5 due to his exhibiting sore throat and diarrhea, wherein he tested negative for the virus. He was transferred to a surgical ward on August 6 upon experiencing surgical issues, and developed fever on the same day. He was transferred to observation ward on August 8, tested positive for the virus, and was transferred to isolation ward for treatment.

detail_zh: 患者於 7 月 22 日因上呼吸道感染入院，曾與第 #3714 宗個案患者入住普通內科病房同一病格，因而被列為密切接觸者，8 月 4 日接受病毒測試結果為陰性。患者於 8 月 8 日出現發燒及咳嗽症狀，8 月 9 日被安排轉到隔離病房再作病毒化驗，結果為陽性。其後病情隨後持續惡化，延至 8 月 11 日下午 12 時 46 分離世。
detail_en: The patient was admitted to hospital on July 22 due to upper respiratory infection, and stayed at the same cubicle with patient #3714 at medical ward, therefore listed as a close contact. He tested negative for the virus on August, and developed fever and coughs on August 8. On August 9, he was transferred to an isolation ward and tested positive. His conditions deteriorated and he passed away at 12:46 p.m., August 11.

detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions, with no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on August 4. He was hospitalised on August 9 upon developing coughs, sore throat, and epigastric pain. His conditions deteriorated, and he passed away at 8:05 a.m., September 2.

detail_en: The patient is an Indonesian domestic helper, has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on August 2. After her previous contract, she helped took care of an elderly individual in Shau Kei Wan for her friend between July 16 and 23. Between July 23 and Aug 3, she stayed temporarily in a dormitory/boarding house on the 9th floor of Cheong Hing Mansion, 15 Cheong Wong Road, Mong Kok. On Aug 3, she started her new job taking caring of two elderly individuals in Tai Kok Tsui.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，8 月 1 日因腸胃問題入住廣華醫院普通外科病房，當時沒有發燒及呼吸道感染徵狀，3 日因發燒被安排入住監察病房及接受測試，結果為陰性，其後被轉到普通外科病房繼續接受治療，並於 8 月 4 日出院。患者於 8 月 8 日因發燒及咳嗽到廣華醫院急症室求診，醫生診斷後為患者安排測試但無需留院，其交還之樣本經化驗後，8 月 9 日初步確診。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history, and was admitted to a surgical ward at Kwong Wah Hospital on August 1 upon developing gastrointestinal problems, having then exhibited no fever or respiratory symptoms. He developed fever three days later, was arranged to a observation ward, and tested negative for the virus. He was transferred to a surgical ward and was discharged on August 4. He visited the Department of Accident and Emergency at Kwong Wah Hospital upon experiencing fever and coughs, and he was arranged for a test but no hospitalisation. His sample tested preliminarily positive for the virus on August 9.

She exhibited no symptoms.(On August 15, she was listed as a confirmed asymptomatic case.)

She wore a mask throughout the exam and was escorted back home by her classmates. She also previously attended a gathering on August 8 and was present on campus on August 10.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者有長期病患，為耆康會啟業護理安老院院友。8 月 10日開始於樟木頭老人度假中心檢疫，8 月 17 日因發燒及血含氧量低入院接受治療，病情其後持續惡化，延至8 月29 日下午 1 時 02 分離世。患者在安老院時與第 #4085 及 #4179 宗個案患者同住。
detail_en: The patient had underlying health conditions and was a resident at The Hong Kong Society for the Aged Kai Yip Home for the Elderly, and began quarantine on August 10 at Cheung Muk Tau Holiday Centre for the Elderly. On August 17 she was hospitalised due to fever and low blood oxygen. Her condition continued to deteriorate, and she passed away on Aug 29 afternoon at 1:02pm. She was a roommate at the Home for the Elderly with patients #4085 and #4179.

detail_zh: 患者屬葵涌貨櫃碼頭群組，為一名貨櫃車司機，主要在車上吃飯及休息，未有使用碼頭的休息室及其他公共設施，因此未能確定患者是於社區還是碼頭感染。因居於慈雲山，曾在 7 月尾接受過民政處的測試，當時呈陰性，8 月 21 日再次遞交樣本後確診。患者無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient belongs to the Kwai Tsing Container Terimals cluster, working as a container truck driver. As he mainly eats and rests on his vehicle and has not used the rest stations and other communal failities at the Terminals, it is uncertain whether the virus was transmitted through community or the Terminals. On account of being a resident at Tsz Wan Shan, he undertook a virus test in late July arranged by  Home Affairs Department and tested negative. He tested positive on August 21 upon resubmission of sample. He has no travel history and exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為印傭，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，7 月 27 日因白血病預約入住東區醫院內科病房化療，入院時對檢測呈陰性，肺片正常。她雖有發燒，但醫生估計與白血病有關。同日僱主（第 #2979 宗個案患者）在養和醫院對檢測呈初步陽性，並轉往東區醫院，翌日確診。患者 8 月 3 日肺片正常，9 日發燒且少許肺花，13 日少許乾咳。8 月 18 至 20 日，印傭曾被安排到單人病房留醫，22 日發高燒，肺片更花，院方再安排檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient is an Indian domestic helper with no recent travel history and no symptoms. On July 27, she was admitted to the Pamela Youde Nethersole Eastern Hospital internal medicine ward for chemotherapy due to leukemia. Upon admission her virus test was negative and her lungs were normal. She had a fever, which the doctor attributed to be related to the leukemia. On the same day, her employer (patient #2979) tested positive at Hong Kong Sanatorium & Hospital and was transferred to the Pamela Youde Nethersole Eastern Hospital. The diagnosis was confirmed the next day. The patient's lungs were normal on Aug 3. On Aug 9, the X-rays of her lungs were cloudy and on Aug 13, she developed a dry cough. Between Aug 18 and 20, she was arranged to stay in a single-person ward. On Aug 22, she developed high fever and the X-rays of her lungs were cloudy. The hospital arranged for subsequent testing and confirmed her diagnosis.

Her husband and son (patients #4763 and #4761) have also tested positive. Her daughter and other son have tested negative, however the son has exhibited the presence of antibodies to the virus.

detail_en: The patient is the husband of patient #4762 and the father of patient #4761. He has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Aug 16. He was hospitalized via ambulance on Aug 26 at around 3pm in the afternoon. At the time he had lost consciousness and was in poor condition. He immediately required CPR and intubation. He passed away at 3:45pm.

detail_zh: 患者有長期病患，與第 #4846 宗個案患者同住於旺角維景酒店等候回中國，8 月 27 日凌晨朋友發現患者頭暈叫救護車送往廣華醫院。患者於送院期間已昏迷，需要急救，至當日凌晨 1 時 39 分病逝，遺體同日早上由食環署人員送往葵涌殮房。
detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions, and was staying at Metropark Hotel Mongkok with patient #4846 awaiting return to China. On August 27 midnight, his friend discovered that he experienced dizziness, and called an ambulance for Kwong Wa Hospital. He was unconscious on the ambulance, requiring first aid, and passed away at 1:39 a.m. on the day. The corpse was transferred to Kwai Chung Public Mortuary by Food and Environmental Hygiene Department staff on the same day.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者

detail_en: The patient is a caretaker at Hong Chi Lei Muk Shue Dormitory, has no recent travel history, and began quarantine at AsiaWorld-Expo on August 24, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者獨居，無外遊紀錄。8 月 28 日曾因腳腫看私家醫生，醫生發現患者血壓高而轉介患者到急症室，但患者沒有前往。8 月 30 日家人聯絡不到患者而報警求助，及後發現患者已死亡，其遺體被送往公眾殮房，抽取肺部組織檢驗後確診。患者生前會到深水埗茶樓飲茶。
detail_en: The patient resides alone and has no travel history. She visited a private practitioner upon developing swollen feet on August 28, and was referred to accident & emergency department due to high blood pressure, but she did not proceed to follow-up. On August 30, her family members contacted the police due to loss of contact with her, and later discovered that she passed away. Her body was transferred to a public mortuary, and the lung tissue sample tested positive for the virus. She used to have dim-sum meals in Sham Shui Po.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，8 月 25 日出現症狀，平常會到大角嘴頌賢花園探訪母親，亦會到竹園邨街市及鳳凰新村富城酒家。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and developed symptoms on August 25. She usually visits her mother at June Garden, Tai Kok Tsui, Chuk Yuen Estate Market, and Treasure City Hotpot Seafood Restaurant, Fung Wong New Village.

detail_zh: 患者 6 月後沒上班，與妻子、家人住荔景山路華豐園，有時去葵盛西邨住所，平日會去保安道街市、北河街街市、美孚街市，8 月 24 日曾到深水埗鴻裕大廈收租。他無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，9 月 1 日參與全民檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient has not worked since July, resides at Wah Fung Garden, Lai King Hill Road with his wife and family members, and often goes to his residence at Kwai Shing West Estate. He usually visits Po On Street Market, Pei Ho Street Market, and Mei Foo Market. He has no travel history and exhibited no symptoms. He went to Hung Yu Mansion, Sham Shui Po to collect rents on August 24, and tested positive after attending the Universal Community Testing Programme on September 1.

detail_zh: 患者無業，有時去觀塘順利紀律部隊宿舍朋友家中，也有出街及外出食飯。她無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，9 月 1 日參與全民檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient is unemployed and often visits a friend at Shun Lee Disciplined Services Quarters, Kwun Tong, goes out, and dines outside home. She has no travel history, exhibited no symptoms, and tested positive after attending the Universal Community Testing Programme.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。

detail_en: The patient is a clerk at 3hreesixty, Elements, and has no direct contact with customers. He has no travel history and developed symptoms on August 22.

detail_en: The patient stayed with patient #4829 at Metropark Hotel Mongkok for several months, and was transferred to quarantine centre on September 1 after patient #4829 was diagnosed. She has no travel history and exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者與家人同住，已退休，間中會到油麻地街市，8月 18 至 22 日曾發燒，22 日輕微腹瀉，沒有求診後痊癒，9 月 1 日參與全民檢測後確診，當時沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides with her family, is a retired person, and occasionally goes to Yau Ma Tei Market. She developd fever between August 18 and 22, and mild diarrhea on August 22, and recovered without medical examination. She tested positive after attending the Universal Community Testing Programme on September 1, then having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient is a housewife, with no travel history, and wife of patient #4854. She attended the Universal Community Testing Programme at Wo Hing Sports Centre, Fanling on September 1, and developed fever next day.

detail_en: The patient stays at Metropark Hotel Mongkok, on the same floor of the previous three patients who do not know one another. He has no travel history and developed symptoms on September 1.

detail_zh: 患者居於鑽石山鳳德邨雪鳳樓，為車房維修工人，於土瓜灣工作，平日在土瓜灣一帶食肆用膳，無外遊紀錄，9 月 1 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides in Fung Tak Estate Block 5 Suet Fung House, Diamond Hill and works as a garage maintenace worker in To Kwa Wan. He eats in restaurants in To Kwa Wan on weekdays. He has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Sept 1.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #4851 宗個案患者的丈夫，居於粉嶺華心邨華勉樓，在大圍交通城地下管理處任職保安，8 月 24 日工作期間曾與第 #4824 宗個案患者因大廈漏水問題見面 10 多分鐘，當時有戴口罩，但第 #4824 宗個案患者沒戴口罩。他無外遊紀錄，8 月 27 日曾到威爾斯親王醫院接受藥物治療，但 8 月 26 日的檢測結果呈陰性，9 月 2 日出現發燒症狀，同日到粉嶺和興體育館接受全民檢測採樣。
detail_en: The patient is the husband of patient #4851, residing at Wah Min House, Wah Sum Estate, Fanling, and works at the management office at Transport City Building, Tai Wai as a security guard. On August 24, he met patient #4824 regarding a leakage problem for around 10 minutes, himself with a mask whereas patient #4824 does not have a mask on. He has no travel history, visited Prince of Wales Hospital on August 27 for pharmacological treatment, but tested negative for the virus on August 26. He developed fever on September 2, and attended the Universal Community Testing Programme at Wo Hing Sports Centre, Fanling on the same day.

detail_en: The patient is a plumbing and electrical artisan, provides air-conditioning engineering services on Nga Tsin Long Road, Kowloon City, and resides at Chi Lan Yuen, 173 Argyle Street. He tested positive for the virus through the Universal Community Testing Programme, with no travel history, and developed symptoms on August 31.

detail_en: The patient is part of a family cluster, resides in Wo Ming Court Wo Yat House in Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history, and no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為菲傭，與僱主住在元朗大井圍村屋，8 月 29 至 30 日曾到元朗媽廟路水邊圍邨與同鄉聚會，為全民檢測的確診個案，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a domestic helper from the Philippines and resides with her employer in Tai Tseng Wai Village, Yuen Long. On Aug 29 and 30, she had been to Shui Pin Wai Estate, Ma Miu Road, Yuen Long in a gathering with other residents of the estate. She is one of the confirmed cases from the Universal Community Testing Programme. She has no recent travel history and no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 4 日由西班牙抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Spain on Sept 4 and has no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者與家人 （第 #4873 宗個案患者） 及外傭 （第 #4872 宗個案患者）同住，無外遊記錄，8 月 29 日出現症狀。曾數度到馮建華醫生診所求診，9 月 2 日到官涌體育館接受全民檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides with her family member (patient #4873) and foreign domestic helper (patient #4872). She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Aug 29. She had been to the clinic of Dr. Fung Kin Wah several times for consultation and was tested positive through the Universal Community Testing Programme at the Kwun Chung Sports Centre, Jordan testing centre on Sept 2.

detail_zh: 患者為懷孕 36 周孕婦，沒有病徵。8 月 21 日乘搭 QR818 由巴基斯坦經多哈回港，抵港後與丈夫及兒子入住酒店進行家居檢疫，9 月 3 日檢疫期滿返回住所。9 月 4 日早上到醫院接受預約產前檢查，為審慎起見醫護人員安排患者轉到隔離病房並接受病毒測試。患者於產前病房逗留了約 45 分鐘，曾經使用病人洗手間，其餘時間留在診症室，同房沒有其他病人。
detail_en: The patient is 36 weeks pregnant and exhibited no symptoms. On August 21 she arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Doha by flight QR818, and stayed at a hotel along with her husband and son for compulsory home quarantine. She returned to her residence on September 3, and visited a hospital on September 4 to book an appointment for for antenatal checkup. The hospital staff transferred her to an isolation ward for a virus test, and she stayed at the antenatal ward for around 45 minutes, having used the patients' toilet, with no presence of other patients.

detail_zh: 患者為懲教署荔枝角收押所的在囚人士，8 月 29 日出現症狀。患者於 8 月 21 日被判處還押到小欖精神病治療中心索取精神科報告，院所管方按既定機制將他隔離，期間與另外一名新收納在囚人士被隔離於同一囚室，二人並無接觸其他在囚人士，並一直有進行體溫探測，體溫正常。9 月 4 日被送往西九龍法院應訊，其後被轉送到茘枝角收押所。抵達院所後，院所管方發現他身體不適及發燒，隨即將他送院接受治療。
detail_en: The patient is a detainee at Lai Chi Kok Reception Centre, and developed symptoms on August 29. On August 21 he was sentenced to Siu Lam Psychiatric Centre to obtain a psychiatric report, and he was quarantined with another newly-arrived detainee in the same cell. Both of whom had no contact with other detainees and had normal body temperature. On September 4 he was transferred to West Kowloon Magistrates' Courts for a hearing, and then Lai Chi Kok Reception Centre, where he was found to have developed discomfort and fever, and then hospitalised.

detail_zh: 患者與僱主（第 #4867 及 #4873 宗個案患者）同住，無外遊記錄，8 月 22 日出現喉嚨痛症狀。曾數度到馮建華醫生診所求診，9 月 2 日到官涌體育館接受全民檢測後確診。

She had been to the clinic of Dr. Fung Kin Wah several times for consultation and was tested positive through the Universal Community Testing Programme at the Kwun Chung Sports Centre, Jordan testing centre on Sept 2.

detail_en: The patient is a retired person, with no travel history, and developed symptoms on August 20. He began staying at L'hotel Nina due to renovation work at his home, and he normally visits dim-sum restaurants around Tsuen Wan and Meifoo.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 4 日由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines and developed symptoms on Sept 4.

detail_zh: 患者為泰籍被羈留人士，沒有病徵，7 月中曾與第 #3741 宗個案患者見面及用餐， 7 月 31 日被判處入獄 8 周，懲教署按既定機制安排患者在荔枝角收押所接受隔離觀察，其間有進行體溫探測，體溫正常。8 月 22 日，患者被轉送到壁屋監獄繼續服刑，其間被安排於處理及清洗污衣的工場工作，負責清洗醫管局轄下醫院的污衣，當中包括病人使用過的衣服、床單被袋等。9 月 4 曰患者服刑完畢由壁屋監獄轉送青山灣入境事務中心等候遣返，因疫情關係，所有新進入中心的被羈留人士均須接受毒病測試，檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a detainee of Thai nationality and has no symptoms. In mid-July he met and dined with patient #3741, He was sentenced for imprisonment for eight weeks on July 31, and was quarantined at Lai Chi Kok Reception Centre, where his temperature checks were normal. On August 22, he was transferred to Pik Uk Prison and assigned to undertake laundry work. He was responsible for the laundry from hospitals under Hospital Authority, including clothing and beddings used by patients. On September 4, upon the end of his detention period he was transferred to Castle Peak Bay Immigration Centre awaiting deportation, and tested positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者由印度抵港，9 月 4 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India and developed symptoms on Sept 4.

detail_zh: 患者於灣仔道金陵會工作，無外遊記錄，9 月 2 日出現症狀，曾到私人診所求診，9 月 4 日於彩雲社區中心接受全民檢測後確診。患者所工作餐廳於 7 月中已暫停營業，餐廳準備進行大清潔後重開，故要求員工於復工前先做檢測。
detail_en: The patient works in Jin Lin Palace on Wan Chai road, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on Sept 2. He had visited a private clinic for consultation. On Sept 4, he tested positive through the Universal Community Testing Programme at the testing centre in Home Affairs Department Choi Wan Estate Community Centre, Ngau Chi Wan. The restaurant the patient worked at has been temporarily closed since mid-July. The restaurant planned to reopen after deep cleaning and requested employees to get tested before returning to work.

detail_zh: 患者為懷孕 33 周孕婦，於太子道西普濟堂中醫診所任職中藥配藥員。患者無外遊記錄，9 月 3 日接受全民檢測，5 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is 33 weeks pregnant and works as a Chinese medicine dispenser at Po Chai Tong Chinese Clinic, Prince Edward Road East. She has no travel history, attended the Universal Community Testing Programme on September 3, and developed symptoms on September 5.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者於大圍交通城 6 樓一商戶工作，無外遊記錄，9 月 3 日接受全民檢測，同日出現疲累症狀。患者曾於 8 月25 或 26 日與第 #4824 宗個案患者交談。
detail_en: The patient works at a unit on 6/F, Transport City Building, with no travel history, and attended the Universal Community Testing Programme on September 3, having developed fatigue on the same day. He previously had a conversation with patient #4824 on August 25 or 26.

detail_zh: 患者已退休，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。患者於 9 月 3 日接受全民檢測，平常會到楊屋道街市外檔攤買菜。
detail_en: The patient is a retired person, with no travel history, and exhibited no symptoms. He attended the Universal Community Testing Programme on September 3, and usually buys grocery at the stalls outside Yeung Uk Road Market.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者於大圍交通城地下管理處工作，為 #4854 宗個案患者的同事，被列為緊密接觸者，無外遊記錄，9 月 3 日出現症狀。衞生署在進行個案追蹤時將患者送往威爾斯親王醫院，患者家人 ( 第 #4889 及 #4890 宗個案患者 ) 同日確診，一名非同住家人（第 #4893 宗個案患者）亦於 9 月 8 日確診。
detail_en: The patient works at Transport City Building, Tai Wai, and as a colleague of patient #4854 is listed as a close contact. He has no travel history and developed symptoms on September 3. He was transferred to Prince of Wales Hospital during the tracking process by Department of Health, and his family members (#4889 and #4890) are diagnosed positive for the virus on the same day as well. A family member who does not live with him (patient #4893) tested positive on September 8.

detail_zh: 患者於牛頭角嘉豪酒家任職管理工作，無外遊記錄，9 月 2 日出現症狀。患者接受全民檢測後確診，平常會獨自進食早餐及午餐，曾因發燒看過醫生。
detail_en: The patient is a manager at Ka Ho Restaurant, Ngau Tau Kok, with no travel history, and developed symptoms on September 2. The patient tested positive after attending the Universal Community Testing Programme. He usually has breakfast and lunch on his own, and previously visited a private practitioner upon developng fever.

detail_zh: 患者為家庭主婦，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。9 月 5 日接受全民檢測，平常會到虹道天橋晨運及牛池灣街市買菜。
detail_en: The patient is a housewife, with no travel history, and exhibited no symptoms. She attended the Universal Community Testing Programme on September 5, and she usually does morning exercises on Choi Hung Road footbridge and buys grocery at Ngau Chi Wan Market.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，沒有病徵，於檢疫中心確診，家人為早前確診個案。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history, exhibited no symptoms, and tested positive at quarantine centre. His family members are patients of earlier confirmed cases.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，為第 #4854 宗個案患者的密切接觸者，送往檢疫時沒有病徵，在檢疫中心接受檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and is a close contact of patient #4854. He exhibited no symptoms while transferred to quarantine centre, where he tested positive for the virus.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，9 月1 日出現症狀，是第 #4884 及 #4890 宗個案患者的家人，在衞生署進行個案追蹤時被送往仁濟醫院。一名非同住家人（第 #4893 宗個案患者）其後於 9 月 8 日確診。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and developed symptoms on September 1. He is a family member of patients #4884 and #4890, and was transferred to Yan Chai Hospital during the tracking process by Department of Health. A family member who does not live with him (patient #4893) tested positive on September 8.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，8 月 31 日出現症狀，是第 #4884 及 #4889 宗個案患者的家人，在衞生署進行個案追蹤時被送往仁濟醫院。一名非同住家人（第 #4893 宗個案患者）其後於 9 月 8 日確診。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and developed symptoms on August 31. She is a family member of patients #4884 and #4889, and was transferred to Yan Chai Hospital during the tracking process by Department of Health. A family member who does not live with her (patient #4893) tested positive on September 8.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，9 月 6 日由烏克蘭抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor, arrived in Hong Kong from Ukraine on Sept 6, and has no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為大圍交通城工業大廈的清潔工，9 月 6 日入住檢疫中心，檢測樣本呈陽性反應。她無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a janitor in Transport City Building, Tai Wai, and was admitted to the quarantine centre on Sept 6. Her virus test came out positive. She has no recent travel history and no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #4884、#4889 及 #4890 宗個案案者的非同住家人，8 月下旬 / 9 月上旬曾與早前確診的家人見面，在家人確診前於 9 月 5 日到大窩口體育館接受全民檢測。她無外遊紀錄，9 月 3 出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patients #4884, #4889, and #4890, whom she does not live with. In late Aug/early Sept, she met with her family members who were diagnosed earlier. Prior to her family members' diagnosis, she went to the testing centre at Tai Wo Hau Sports Centre and participated in the Universal Community Testing Programme on Sept 5. She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Sept 3.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，9 月 5 日於兆麟社區中心接受全民檢測，沒有病徵，平日會到置樂街市、友愛街市等購物。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and was tested in the Universal Community Testing Programme on Sept 5 at the Tuen Mun Siu Lun Community Centre. She has no symptoms, and goes shopping on the weekdays, including to Yan Oi Market and Yo Mart.

detail_zh: 患者 8 月 28 日由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Phililppines on Aug 28 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 8 月 28 日由菲律賓抵港，9 月 2 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Phililppines on Aug 28 and developed symptoms on Sept 2.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為大圍交通城保安家人，無外遊紀錄，8 月 30 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of a security guard in Transport City Building, Tai Wai, has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Aug 30.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為早前確診者的密切接觸者，無外遊紀錄，9 月 3 日出現症狀，入住檢疫中心後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a close contact of a past confirmed case, has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on Sept 3, and was diagnosed after admission to the quarantine centre.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為大圍交通城職員家人，無外遊紀錄，9 月 6 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of an employee in Transport City Building, Tai Wai, has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Sept 6.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為早前確診者的密切接觸者，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，入住檢疫中心後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a close contact of a past confirmed case, has no recent travel history, no symptoms, and was diagnosed after admission to the quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，間中會在住所附近飲茶。他在 9 月 6 日於屯門大興社區會堂接受全民檢測，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and would occasionally have dimsum near his area of residence. On Sept 6, he was tested in the Universal Community Testing Programme at the Home Affairs Department Tai Hing Community Hall in Tuen Mun. He has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由印度抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者與家人 ( 第 #4904 及 #4905 宗個案患者 ) 於 9 月 8 日乘搭 AI314 由印度抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong with family members (patients #4904 and #4905) on Sept 8 from India on flight AI314, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者與家人 ( 第 #4903 及 #4905 宗個案患者 ) 於 9 月 8 日乘搭 AI314 由印度抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong with family members (patients #4903 and #4905) on Sept 8 from India on flight AI314, and has no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong with family members (patients #4903 and #4904) on Sept 8 from India on flight AI314, and has no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 8 from India on flight AI314, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 8 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 8 from the Philippines on flight CX906, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者乘搭 QR818 由伊朗經卡塔爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Iran via Qatar on flight QR818 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者於 9 月 8 日乘搭 AI314 由印度抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 8 from India on flight AI314, and has no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，8 月 31 日出現症狀，於檢疫中心確診，家人為早前的確診者。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on Aug 31, was diagnosed in the quarantine centre, and had a family member who was previously diagnosed.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，9 月 8 日出現症狀，於檢疫中心確診，家人為早前的確診者。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on Sept 8, was diagnosed in the quarantine centre, and had a family member who was previously diagnosed.

detail_zh: 患者於百德新街一食肆工作，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵，最近上班日期為 9 月 6 日。患者於 9 月 7 日於官涌體育館接受全民檢測，8 日陪同兒子（第 #4918 宗個案患者）到伊利沙伯醫院交回深喉唾液樣本，9 日再陪同兒子到眼科醫院接受手術，於兒子手術期間獲知初步確診。母子二人在 9 月 10 日接受血清抗體測試，結果呈陽性，代表二人可能較早前已受感染。患者與丈夫及兒子居於油麻地廟街，平常多到油麻地街市購物。
detail_en: The patient works at a resutrant on Paterson Street, with no travel history and having displayed no symptoms, and last attended work on September 6. She attended the Universial Community Testing Programme at Kwun Chung Sports Centre on September 7, and accompanied her son (patient #4918) to turn in a deep throat saliva sample at Queen Elizabeth Hospital on September 8. She accompanied her son at Hong Kong Eye Hospital who had an operation on September 9, and received notification regarding her diagnosis during his operation. Both of them took a serologic test on September 10 and tested positive, meaning that they may have been infected earlier on. The patient and her husband and son live on Temple Street, Yaumatei, and usually shops at Yau Ma Tei Market.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，9 月 8 日出現症狀，於檢疫中心確診，家人為早前的確診者。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on Sept 8, was diagnosed in the quarantine centre, and had a family member who was previously diagnosed.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，9 月 1 日出現症狀。患者於元朗一食肆任職侍應，9 月 8 日在新界鄉議局元朗區中學接受全民檢測，平常多到合益街市購物。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and developed symptoms on September 1. She works as a waitress at a restaurant in Yuen Long, and attended the Universal Community Testing Programme at New Territories Heung Yee Kuk Yuen Long District Secondary School. She usually shops at Hop Yick Market.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor, arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 9 日乘坐 HX782 航班由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 9 from the Philippines on flight HX782, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 9 日乘坐 HX782 航班由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 9 from the Philippines on flight HX782, and has no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #4912 宗個案患者的兒子。因要接受眼部手術，9 月 8 日到伊利沙伯醫院提交深喉唾液樣本，測試結果呈陰性；9 日在香港眼科醫院接受手術，其間其母接獲確診通知，患者手術後再接受深喉唾液測試結果變為陽性。母子二人在 9 月 10 日接受血清抗體測試，結果呈陽性，代表二人可能較早前已受感染。
detail_en: The patient is the son of patient #4912 and turned in a deep throat saliva sample at Queen Elizabeth Hospital on September 8 prior to his eye operation, which tested negative for the virus. During his operation on September 9 at Hong Kong Eye Hospital, his mother received notification regarding her diagnosis during his operation. He re-tested after the operation with deep throat saliva sample and tested positive. Both of them took a serologic test on September 10 and tested positive, meaning that they may have been infected earlier on.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 9 日乘坐 HX782 航班由菲律賓抵港，9 月 9 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 9 from the Philippines on flight HX782, and developed symptoms on Sept 9.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 9 日乘坐 HX782 航班由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 9 from the Philippines on flight HX782, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 9 日乘坐 HX782 航班由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 9 from the Philippines on flight HX782, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為家庭主婦，9 月 7 日在將軍澳翠林體育館接受全民檢測，沒有病徵，日常會到新都城街市買菜。
detail_en: The patient is a housewife and attended Universal Community Testing Programme at Tsui Lam Sports Centre on September 7, having exhibited no symptoms. She usually shops at Metro City Plaza Market.

detail_zh: 患者由英國返港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為貨機機師，由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a cargo pilot, arrived in Hong Kong from the US, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為旺角維景酒店海港酒家的樓面，平日上班獨自用膳，居於旺角通菜街，平日會去旺角街市；8 月 31 日出現症狀，9  月9 日到界限街一號體育館參與全民檢測。
detail_en: The patient is a waitress at Victoria Harbour Restaurant, Pioneer Centre and dines on her own at work. She lives on Tung Choi Street, Mongkok, and usually goes to Mong Kok Market. She developd symptoms on August 31 and attended Universal Community Testing Programme at Boundary Street Sports Centre No.1.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，9 月 5 日出現症狀。患者於屯門 18 咪半黃金泳灘 L’atlantis 餐廳工作，最近上班日期為 9 月 9 日。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and developed symptoms on September 5. She works at the restaurant L'atlantis at Gold Coast, and last attended work on September 9.

detail_zh: 患者為退休人士，無外遊記錄，與 6 名家人居於油塘油麗邨雅麗樓，其中 3 名家人 ( 第 #4933、#4934 及 #4935 宗個案患者 ) 亦於同日確診。患者於 9 月 4 日出現喉嚨痛症狀，9 日到聯合醫院急症室求診，10 日交回樣本作檢測。平常會到觀塘新港明珠酒家、裕民坊附近公園及鯉魚門街市。
detail_en: The patient is a retired person with no travel history, and resides at Nga Lai House, Yau Lai Estate, Yau Tong with six other family members, three of whom (patients #4933, #4934, and #4935) were also diagnosed on the same day. The patient developed sore throat on September 4, visited the accident & emergency department at United Christian Hospital on September 9, and turned in a sample on September 10. He usually goes to New Harbour Pearl Seafood Restaurant at Kwun Tong, parks around Yue Man Square, and Lei Yue Mun Market.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月10 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines on September 10 by flight CX906, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月10 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。

detail_en: The patient is an Indian sailor arriving in Hong Kong from London by flight BA31, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由俄羅斯經土耳其抵港，9 月 9 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Russia via Turkey and developed symptoms on September 9.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，與 6 名家人居於油塘油麗邨雅麗樓，其中 3 名家人 ( 第 #4928、#4934 及 #4935 宗個案患者 ) 亦於同日確診。患者 9 月 9 日於鯉魚門體育館接受全民檢測，10 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and resides at Nga Lai House, Yau Lai Estate, Yau Tong with six other family members, three of whom (patients #4928, #4934, and #4935) were also diagnosed on the same day. He attended the Universal Community Testing Programme at Lei Yue Mun Sports Centre on September 9, and developed symptoms on September 10.

detail_en: The patient is a retired person, with no travel history, and lives with his family members. He developed symptoms on September 1. He passed away on Nov 9 evening at 9:15pm.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，9 月 8 日出現症狀，居於樂富邨，於流浮山從事文職工作。她曾於 9 月 6 日與第 #4946 宗個案患者一起到深水埗福華街萬發海鮮菜館用膳。
detail_en: The patient has no travel history and developed symptoms on September 8. She lives in Lok Fu Estate and works as a clerk in Lau Fau Shan. She had shared a meal with patient #4946 on Sept 6 at Man Fat Seafood Restaurant, Fuk Wa Street, Sham Shui Po.

detail_en: The patient had stayed in a room in Metropark Hotel Mongkok on the same floor as another previously diagnosed case. He was hospitalized due to his injuries, and was later transferred to quarantine centre. He was diagnosed while in the quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，9 月 9 日到屯門內科專科門診覆診，醫生建議入院檢查，11 日入住屯門醫院時沒有病徵。住院時因病房入住率超過 100%，一度被安排在走廊的臨時病牀。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and visited Tuen Mun Hospital Internal Medicine Specialty Clinic for follow-up consultation. The doctor recommended admission to hospital for examination and she was asymptomatic when admitted to Tuen Mun Hospital on Sept 11. During hospitalization, the ward occupancy rate had exceeded full capacity and she was once placed in a temporary bed in the corridor.

He participated in the Universal Community Testing Programme on Sept 10 and was tested at the testing centre in Tai Po Sports Centre.

detail_en: The patient is an Indian domestic helper who received testing with her employer on Sept 10 through the Universal Community Testing Programme at the testing centre in Home Affairs Department Lai King Community Hall, Kwai Chung. She has no symptoms. On weekdays she goes shopping on Mei Foo Sun Chuen Market, and usually stay at her residence during Sundays as well.

On the same day, she was tested in the Universal Community Testing Programme at the testing centre in Leung Tin Sports Centre, Tuen Mun. She was hospitalized when patient #4946 tested positive. When she was in the Accident & Emergency Department, her results came out preliminary positive.

He frequented Do Shing Restaurant, Tuen Mun often for breakfast and developed symptoms Sept 6. Another family member whom he lives with (patient #4981) has also been diagnosed.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 5 日由倫敦乘國泰航空 CX252 航班抵港，6 日出現症狀，檢疫期間第二個檢測樣本呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 5 from London on Cathay Pacific flight CX252, developed symptoms on Sept 6, and tested positive on the second test during quarantine.

detail_zh: 患者為印尼籍外傭，無外遊記錄，與僱主同住，平常較少外出。9 月 14 日放假曾與朋友到旺角、深水埗及尖沙咀逛街及用膳，9 月 15 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is an Indonesian domestic helper, with no recent travel history, resides with her employer, and does no frequently go out. On her day off on September 14 she walked around and dined at Mongkok, Sham Shui Po, and Tsim Sha Tsui along with her friends, and then developed symptoms on September 15.

detail_zh: 患者為退休人士，無外遊紀錄，9 月 11 日開始發燒，12 至 15 日都留在家，其間有家人前往探望，平日會到愛定商場大家樂吃早餐。其家人（第 #5038 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a retired person with no recent travel history. She developed fever on September 11 and stayed home between September 12 and 15 when she was visited by her family members. She usually has breakfast at Café de Coral, H.A.N.D.S (Tuen Mun). Her family member (patient #5038) was later on diagnosed positive as well.

detail_zh: 患者任職香港大學公共衞生學院研究員，在港大醫學院實驗室樓 6 樓工作，主要處理電腦資料的文書工作包括病毒的基因排序，亦曾處理武漢肺炎病毒的滅活樣本，14 日潛伏期內沒處理具傳染性樣本。她無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，潛伏期曾與朋友吃飯及外出。
detail_en: The patient is a researcher at School of Public Health, University of Hong Kong, working on 6/F, Laboratory Block, Faculty of Medicine Building. She is mainly responsible for clerical tasks including the genetic sequencing of the virus, and also handled inactivated samples of the coronavirus. She did not handle infectious samples during the 14-day incubation period. She has no recent travel history, exhibited no symptoms, and dined with her friends outside during the incubation period.

She shops for grocery at T Market (Chung Fu, Tin Shui Wai) one to two days a week, and every weekend stays at a room she rents at Ma Tin Pok, Yuen Long, with shared bathroom.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者有長期病患，需要定時接受治療，最近一次是在 9 月 18 日上午，在屯門醫院兒科病房逗留近兩小時。患者當時沒有呼吸道感染徵狀，大部分時間有佩戴口罩。他無外遊紀錄，9 月 19 日出現症狀，21 日深夜因出現呼吸道感染徵狀，到屯門醫院急症室求診，再轉送兒科隔離病房留醫。其外傭（第 #5041 宗個案患者）早前確診。
detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions and requires regular treatment. He had most recently stayed in the pediatric ward in Tuen Mun Hospital on Sept 18 morning for nearly two hours. He had no symptoms of respiratory tract infection at the time and had worn his mask for most of the time. He has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Sept 19. On Sept 21, he developed respiratory infection symptoms late at night and went to the Accident & Emergency Department of Tuen Mun Hospital for consultation. He was then transferred to the pediatric isolation ward for treatment. His foreign domestic helper (#5041) was earlier diagnosed positive for the virus.

He visited the accident & emergency department at Caritas Medical Centre on September 25, and the sample he turned in on September 26 tested positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者為元朗護老院院友，有認知障礙症，沒有病徵，原居於觀塘翠屏邨翠楣樓，並曾因遺失身份證到警署。9 月 21 日入住元朗護老院，在院舍內可自由活動，經常不戴口罩，28 日因其他原因入院，對病毒測試呈陽性，病毒量低，病毒抗體亦呈陽性，估計較早前於觀塘受感染。
detail_en: The patient is a resident at Yuen Long Home for the Elderly, with dementia, having exhibited no symptoms. She originally resided at Tsui Mei House, Tsui Ping (North) Estate, Kwun Tong, and visited a police station upon loss of identity card. She began her residence at Yuen Long Home for the Elderly on September 21, and is fully mobile and often does not wear a mask. She was hospitalised for other reasons on September 28 and tested positive for the virus. She has a low viral load and tested positive for the antibodies, and so it is speculated that she was infected earlier on in Kwun Tong.

detail_zh: 患者為菲傭，沒有病徵，9 月 8 日抵港後首個樣本，以及 9 月 17 日取的第二個樣本，均對病毒呈陰性；抵港在酒店完成檢疫後，由新僱主安排入住酒店，其間曾外出買外賣；28 日接受第三次測試結果呈陽性，病毒抗體檢測亦呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper from the Philippines and has no symptoms. Her first test sample was taken on Sept 8 after arriving Hong Kong, and the second on Sept 17, both were negative for the virus. After arriving in Hong Kong she completed her quarantine in a hotel. Her new employer arranged for her to continue staying in a hotel, during which she went out to buy takeout. On Sept 28 she was tested for the third time. The third test came out positive, and the antibody test was also positive.

detail_zh: 患者為菲傭，9 月 18 日抵港，檢疫期間第二個樣本檢測結果呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines on September 18, and her second sample during quarantine tested positive for the virus. She exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 18 日由印度抵港，檢疫期間第二個樣本檢測結果呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on September 18, and her second sample during quarantine tested positive for the virus. She exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者與第 #5088 宗個案患者一同由英國抵港，9 月 19 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK along with patient #5088, and developed symptoms on September 19.

detail_zh: 患者與第 #5087 宗個案患者一同由英國抵港，9 月 29 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK along with patient #5087, and developed symptoms on September 29.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日乘搭 CX216 由英國抵港，9 月 27 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK on Sept 29 on flight CX216 and developed symptoms on Sept 27.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日乘搭 CX216 由英國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK on Sept 29 on flight CX216 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日乘搭 CX216 由英國抵港，9 月 27 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK on Sept 29 on flight CX216 and developed symptoms on Sept 27.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日乘搭 TK070 由英國抵港，同日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK by flight TK070 on September 29, and developed symptoms on the same day.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日乘搭 TK070 由英國抵港，9 月 28 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK by flight TK070 on September 29, and developed symptoms on September 28.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日乘搭 PR300 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight PR300 on September 29, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9  月 6 日由法國抵港，隔離期間居於上環普慶閣，26 日經私家醫生化驗後確診，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from France on September 6, and stayed at Po Hing Court, Sheung Wan during quarantine period. She tested positive for the virus at a visit to a private practitioner, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 22 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港，隔離期間居於尖沙咀維港灣酒店，9 月 29 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight CX906 on September 22, and stayed at Harbour Bay Hotel during quarantine period. She developed symptoms on September 29.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 19 日乘搭 EK384 由杜拜抵港，隔離期間居於大角咀帝峯‧皇殿 2 座。9 月 29 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Dubai by flight EK384 on September 19, and stayed at Tower 2, The Hermitage, Tai Kok Tsui during quarantine period. He developed symptoms on September 29.

detail_zh: 患者為泰國旅客，自 3 月起一直滯留本港，與朋友入住尖沙咀多家酒店；朋友 9 月下旬返泰後，她亦打算離港，惟經檢測後確診。她在潛伏期間，由 8 月至 9 月 26 日病發前住在尖沙咀利園賓館，她在 9 月 27 日轉至觀塘帝盛酒店居住，再於 9 月 28 日轉至觀塘悅品海景酒店，亦曾到尖沙咀海港城等地購物和用膳。
detail_en: The patient is a Thai visitor stranded in Hong Kong since March, and stayed at several hotels in Tsim Sha Tsui with her friend prior to her developing symptoms on September 26, including Lee Garden Guest House. She plans to leave Hong Kong after the recent departure of her friend, but she tested positive for the virus. During her incubation period, she stayed at Lee Garden Guest House from August to September 26, Dorsett Kwun Tong on September 27, and Hotel COZI Harbour View on September 28, and shopped and dined at Harbour City, Tsim Sha Tsui and other places.

detail_zh: 患者為貨機機師，9 月 30 日由德國抵港，9 月 29 日出現症狀，患者亦曾到過俄羅斯、新加坡及杜拜。
detail_en: The patient is a cargo pilot, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 30 from Germany and developed symptoms on Sept 29. He had recently been in Russia, Singapore, and Dubai.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月30 日乘搭 CX222 由英國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 30 from the UK on flight CX222 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，9 月 30 日乘搭 HX782 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 30 from the the Philippines on flight HX782 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者在國際金融中心日本餐廳「無二」任職廚師，主要負責熟食，煮食時有戴口罩，沒有處理刺身等生鮮食物，亦不會接觸食客。他於 9 月 25 日起發燒，最後上班日為 9 月 29 日，9 月 30 日入院，平日通常在灣仔港鐵站附近餐廳購買外賣。
detail_en: The patient works as a chef at Mu-ni by La Bombance, IFC, mainly responsible for cooked food. He wears a mask when cooking, does not handle sashimi and other raw food, and has no contact to customers. He developed fever on September 25, last attended work on September 29, and was hospitalised on September 30. He usually buys takeaway meals nears Wan Chai MTR station.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為早前確診者的家居密切接觸者，9 月 21 日被送到檢疫中心，30 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a close contact with a previously diagnosed patient whom she lived with. She was transferred to the quarantine centre on Sept 21 and developed symptoms on Sept 30.

detail_zh: 患者為伊利沙伯醫院內科病房護士，9 月 28 日開始出現咳嗽，30 日晚上因發燒到急症室求診並接受深喉唾液測試，其後確診。患者與家人同住，9 月18 及 20 日曾到朋友家吃飯。
detail_en: The patient is a medical ward nurse at Queen Elizabeth Hospital and developed coughs on September 28. He visited an accident & emergency department on September 30 evening upon developing fever, and tested positive at a deep throat saliva test. He resides with his family members, and dined at his friend's home on September 18 and 20.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 21 日由尼泊爾抵港，檢疫期間提交的第二次樣本檢測結果呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on Sept 21 and her second test sample during quarantine came out positive. She has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由菲律賓乘搭 CX906 於 10 月 1 日抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Oct 1 from the Philippines on flight CX906 and has no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者就讀香港專業教育學院 （IVE） 將軍澳李惠利分校，9 月 29 日最後一日上學，同日出現咳等病徵，翌日到急症室求診。他於 9 月 23 日曾去尖沙咀利就商業大厦的酒吧 China Secret。其家人（第 #5112 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient studies at Hong Kong Institute of Vocational Education (Lee Wai Lee), Tseung Kwan O, and last attended class on September 29, having developed coughs and other symptoms on the same day. He visited an accident & emergency department next day. On September 23 he went to a bar named China Secret at Lee Chau Commercial Building, Tsim Sha Tsui. His family member (patient #5112) was later on diagnosed as well.

detail_zh: 患者由印度經杜拜乘搭 EK384 於 9 月 30 日抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 30 from India on flight EK384 via Dubai and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由英國經阿姆斯特丹乘搭 KL887 於 9 月 30 日抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong on Sept 30 from the UK on flight KL887 via Amsterdam and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者有長期病患， 9 月 13 日由尼泊爾抵港，抵港後於酒店接受家居檢疫，9 月 25 日曾出現無食慾及胃痛的症狀。9 月 27 日完成家居檢疫後轉往兒子及媳婦（第 #5124 及 #5125 宗個案患者）於炮台街立德大樓的家中居住，28 日被帶往油麻地普通科門診診所求醫，10 月 1 日到於彌敦道 451 號私人診所求診， 2 日因發燒、嘔吐及腹瀉入住伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部，其後確診。患者經治療後，病毒檢測呈陰性。患者因呼吸衰竭須使用呼吸機，並於深切治療部繼續留醫。患者病情其後持續惡化，延至 12 月 2 日中午 12 時 53 分離世。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on September 13, was under compulsory quarantine at a hotel, and developed symptoms on September 25. She stayed at the residence of her son and daughter-in-law (patients #5124 and #5125) at Lap Tak House, Battery Street on September 27 upon completion of quarantine period, and her relatives arranged for her a visit to Yau Ma Tei Jockey Club General Out-patient Clinic on September 28. She then visited a private practitioner at 451 Nathan Road on October 1, and the accident & emergency deparment of Queen Elizabeth Hospital on October 2.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為泰籍家庭主婦，與家人同住於青衣長宏邨宏勇樓，平常會到長發街市及青衣城。9 月 20 及 26 日曾與新認識泰籍朋友 ( 第 #5130 宗個案患者 ) 於尖沙咀逛街。
detail_en: The patient is a housewife of Thai nationality, residing at Wang Yung House, Cheung Wang Estate, Tsing Yi along with her family members. She usually goes to Cheung Fat Market and Maritime Square, Tsing Yi. She visited Tsim Sha Tsui with a newly acquainted Thai friend (patient #5130) on September 20 and 26.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5107 宗個案患者的家人，10 月 2 日入住檢疫中心接受強制檢疫，由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5107, has been under compulsory quarantine since October 2, and was hospitalised from quarantine centre, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為貨機工作人員，10 月 2 日由俄羅斯抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a cargo flight crew member arriveing in Hong Kong from Russia on October 2 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 23 日乘搭 RA409 由尼泊爾抵港，第二次樣本檢測呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA409 on September 23. His second sample tested positive for the virus and he has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由印度經杜拜乘搭 EK384 航班，在 10 月 3 日抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India via Dubai on October 3 by flight EK384, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾乘搭 RA4099 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA4099 on October 3, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾乘搭 RA4099 由尼泊爾抵港，同日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA4099 on October 3 and developed symptoms on the same day.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾乘搭 RA4099 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA4099 on October 3, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾乘搭 RA4099 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA4099 on October 3, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾乘搭 RA4099 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA4099 on October 3, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾乘搭 RA4099 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal by flight RA4099 on October 3, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為文員，在葵涌捷聯大廈工作，平日會到附近買外賣，9 月 14 日曾到尖沙咀港威酒店進食午餐自助餐，取食物時有戴口罩；24 日開始咳嗽；28 日在葵興九龍貿易中心 Oliver's Super Sandwich 吃三文治。
detail_en: The patient works as a clerk in Chiap Luen Industrial Building, Kwai Chung and often bought takeaway food nearby on weekdays. On Sept 14, she had been to Gateway Hotel in Tsim Sha Tsui for buffet lunch and had worn her mask when taking food from the buffet. On Sept 24, she started coughing. On Sept 28, she had been to Oliver's Super Sandwich at Kowloon Commerce Centre in Kwai Hing for sandwiches.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者 3 月中由泰國抵港探望朋友，與 5 人同住由泰籍朋友提供的尖沙咀豪麗大廈單位，其後分別遷往附近的仕德福山景酒店和君怡酒店。其中一名同住友人（第 #5130 宗個案患者）曾與第 #5111 宗個案患者一起逛街。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Thailand in mid-March to visit a friend and stayed with 5 other people in a flat in Holly Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui that was provided by the friend of Thai nationality. She then moved to the nearby Stanford Hillview Hotel and The Kimberley Hotel, both in Tsim Sha Tsui. One of the friends she was living with (patient #5130) had gone shopping with patient #5111.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5110 宗個案患者的兒子，第 #5125 宗個案患者的丈夫，在香港國際社會服務社轄下觀塘的免遣返聲請人辦事處任職外判保安員，主要駐守辦事處入口及等候區。他無外遊紀錄，10 月 3 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is the son of patient #5110 and husband of patient #5125, working as a contract security guard at the International Social Service Hong Kong Branch office for non-refoulement claimants in Kwun Tong, mainly stationed at office entrance and waiting area. He has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on October 3.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5110 宗個案患者的媳婦，第 #5124 宗個案患者的妻子，在香港國際社會服務社擔任文職，於炮台山的免遣返聲請人兒童宿舍上班，最後上班日為 9 月 30 日。她無外遊紀錄，10 月 2 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is the daughter-in-law of patient #5110 and wife of patient #5124, working as a clerk at a children dormitory for non-refoulement claimants in Fortress Hill operated by International Social Service Hong Kong Branch. She last attended work on September 30, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on October 2.

detail_zh: 患者無業，與家人同住北角富家閣。10 月 1 日曾到位於黃埔的親戚家中參與 16 人家庭聚會。10 月 2 日在太古城中心百老匯 MOViE MOViE 戲院看電影，期間有戴口罩，曾光顧炮台山傷心酸辣粉。10 月 3 日出現症狀並到急症室求診。
detail_en: The patient is unemployed and lives with his family in Wealthy Court, North Point. On Oct 1, he had been to a relative's home in Whampoa to attend a family gathering of 16 people. On Oct 2, he had been to MOViE MOViE Cinema in Broadway Tai Koo Shing to watch a movie. He wore a mask during the movie. He had also recently visited Sour and Spicy Noodle restaurant in Fortress Hill. On Oct 3, he developed symptoms and went to the accident & emergency department for treatment.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，10 月 4 日乘搭 HX782 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight HX782 on October 4, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，10 月 4 日乘搭 TK070 由德國經土耳其抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor arriving in Hong Kong from Germany via Turkey by flight TK070 on October 4, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 4 日由俄羅斯經德國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Russia via Germany on October 4, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者 9 月 20 及 26 日曾與第 #5111 宗個案患者於尖沙咀逛街，曾與第 #5123 宗個案患者同住酒店，10 月 4 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient visited Tsim Sha Tsui with patient #5111 on September 20 and 26, stayed at a hotel with patient #5123, and developed symptoms on October 4.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為輸入個案患者的緊密接觸者，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a close contact of a patient of an imported case, with no recent travel history and having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者與家人同住於灣仔謝斐道快添大廈，在尖沙咀帝苑酒店 3 樓的 Le Soleil 越南餐廳任職侍應。10 月 2 日出現症狀，最近上班日期為 10 月 3 日，同日到私人診所求診，10 月 5 日交回樣本檢測。患者有在工作地點的更衣室休息，亦會在酒店員工餐廳用餐。
detail_en: The patient lives with his family in Fasteem Mansion, Jaffe Road, Wan Chai, and works as a waiter in the Vietnamese restaurant Le Soleil on the 3rd floor of Tsim Sha Tsui hotel, The Royal Garden. He developed symptoms on Oct 2 and his last day of work was Oct 3. He also visited a private clinic for consultation on Oct 3. On Oct 5, he submitted a sample for testing. During work, he would rest in the changing rooms of his workplace, and would have meals in the restaurant for hotel staff.

detail_zh: 患者為學生，只需網上上課，與家人同住屯門龍門居第 15 座。10 月 1 日開始發燒，曾到仁愛堂街高富餐廳吃早餐，經常到仁愛堂鄭耀源紀念健體中心健身，期間有戴口罩。10 月 1 日曾到元朗滔滔甜品，10 月 3 日到過屯門新墟譚仔三哥，10 月 4 日曾光顧龍門居雲貴軒，亦曾到過井財街金銘餐廳小廚。患者 10 月 4 日到急症痓求診，10 月 5 日交回樣本作檢測，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a student who only attends online classes, living in Block 15, Lung Mun Oasis with his family members. He developed fever on October 1, and had breakfast a Gaofu Restaurant, Yan Oi Tong Circuit, and frequently visits the gym at Yan Oi Tong Jockey Club Community & Sports Centre where he wears a mask. He dined at Total Dessert, Yuen Long on October 1; TamJai SamGor Mixian at San Hui, Tuen Mun on October 3; The Vermicelli House, Lung Mun Oasis on October 4; and Kam Ming Chiu Chow Restaurant, Tseng Choi Street. He visited an accident & emergency department on October 4, returned a sample for testing on October 5, and was diagnosed positive for the virus on October 5.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者與第 #5141 宗個案患者同居於尖沙咀豪麗大廈，無外遊紀錄，10 月 2 日轉到帝苑酒店居住，10 月 5 日出現症狀，被送往檢疫中心後入院確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Holly Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui with patient #5141, with no recent travel history. She stayed at The Royal Garden from October 2 onwards, developed symptoms on October 5, and was hospitalised upon transfer to quarantine centre.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為西洋菜街龍城中西藥房職員，與第 #5136 及 #5137 宗個案患者為朋友，平常會到其他兩名患者工作藥房交談及借貨。患者最近上班日期為 10 月 4 日，同日出現症狀，10 月 5 日早上到養和醫院求診。患者與家人曾於 9 月 25 日到油塘中心按摩店按摩。
detail_en: The patient works in Dragon City Dispensary on Sai Yeung Choi Street and is friends with patients #5136 and #5137. He usually went to the dispensaries his friends worked at to talk and borrow goods. His last day at work was Oct 4 and he developed symptoms on the same day. On Oct 5 morning, he visited Hong Kong Sanatorium & Hospital for consultation. On Sept 25, he had been to a massage parlor in Yau Tong Centre with his family for a massage.

He usually went to the dispensaries his friends worked at to talk and borrow goods. He developed symptoms on Oct 3 and his last day at work was Oct 4. On Oct 5 morning, he visited Hong Kong Sanatorium & Hospital for consultation. On Sept 30, he had been to a massage parlor with his family to get a massage on Tak Ku Ling Road, Kowloon City.

During the incubation period he attended family gatherings with his elder brother (patient #5143) including group meals and barbecuing, involving around 13 relatives.

She left the premises of the care home several times during the incubation period, having dined at Fairwood, Shek Yam Shopping Centre on October 3; McDonald's, Shek Yam Shopping Centre on October 4; and Golden Cafe, Kwong Fai Building, Shek Yam.

detail_en: The patient is a retired person residing at Braemar Hill Mansions, and goes to gyms every day for classes or workouts. He usually goes to Fitness First at Causeway Bay and Hopewell Centre, Wan Chai, sometimes along with his wife. He previously dined at his relative's home, dined at Queen's Cafe, Island Place on October 2; worked out at Fitness First, Tower 535 on October 3; and Fitness First at Hopewell Centre on October 4.

detail_en: The patient works as a waiter at Sabatini, 3/F, The Royal Garden, with no recent travel history. He was on a day-off on October 5 when the Department of Health distributed sample bottles, and he visited a private practitioner on October 6 upon developing fever. At work he uses a changing room on B3/F shared with other male co-workers, as well as dining at a staff canteen on B3/F shared with all staff members. His family member (patient #5176) was later on diagnosed.

detail_en: The patient is a resident at Home of Treasure, Kwai Chung, developed symptoms on Oct 10 during the quarantine period, and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者 7 月 11 日由巴基斯坦抵港後入住駿洋邨，檢疫期間接受兩次檢測結果均為陰性。8 月 24 日入住廣華醫院，8 月 27 日分娩，8 月 29 日出院，患者於廣華醫院留院期間沒有發燒及上呼吸道病徵故沒有安排檢測。10 月 10 日患者因腰痛再度入院，入院篩查檢測結果呈弱陽性並驗出抗體。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan on July 11 and stayed in Chun Yeung Estate, Fo Tan. During the quarantine period, the test results came out negative on both occasions. On Aug 24, she was hospitalized to Kwong Wah Hospital, gave birth on Aug 27, and was discharged from hospital on Aug 29. The patient had no fever or respiratory symptoms during her stay at Kwong Wah Hospital and thus no testing was arranged. On Oct 10, the patient was admitted to hospital due to lower back pain. The test result from admission screening came out weak positive and antibodies were also detected.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為國寶之家院友，於 10 月 8 日檢疫期間出現症狀，由檢疫中心送院。
detail_en: The patient is a resident at Home of Treasure, Kwai Chung, developed symptoms on Oct 8 during the quarantine period, and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from France on Oct 11 aboard flight LX138 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日與第 #5191 宗個案患者一同乘搭 CX252 由英國抵港，10 月 7 日開始失去味覺。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK on Sept 29 aboard flight CX252 and began to lose sense of taste on Oct 7. Patient #5191 was also on the same flight.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 1 日由瑞士經土耳其抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Switzerland via Turkey on Oct 1 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 9 月 29 日與第 #5189 宗個案患者一同乘搭 CX252 由英國抵港，10 月 7 日開始失去味覺。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK on Sept 29 aboard flight CX252 and began to lose sense of taste on Oct 7. Patient #5189 was also on the same flight.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on Oct 10 and has no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為屯門職業訓練局青年學院學生，10 月 4 日開始失去味覺，10 月 5 日最後一日上學，10 月 8 日自行到政府門診拿樣本瓶檢驗後確診。患者 9 月 27 日曾參與於尖沙咀港威酒店一聚會，其中一名出席者為 China Secret 相關確診個案但本身沒有到過 China Secret。患者在 10 月 3 日曾與社工於粉嶺和興體育館打羽毛球，亦曾於校內與同學用膳。衞生署曾透過警方協助找尋患者不果，其後發現患者已自行求醫。
detail_en: The patient is a student at IVE Youth College, Tuen Mun. She began losing her sense of tasting on October 4, and last attended class on October 5. She obtained a sample bottle from a government General Out-patient Clinic on October 8 and later tested positive for the virus. She attended a gathering at Gateway Hotel, Tsim Sha Tsui on September 27, which was also attended by a patient related to the China Secret cluster but did not go to the bar. The patient played badminton at Wo Hing Sports Centre, Fanling with a social worker on October 3, and also dined on campus with other students. The Department of Health did not successfully locate the patient with the aid of police at first, later realising that the patient sought medical examination herself.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為早前確診個案的緊密接觸者，由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a close contact of one of the previously diagnosed cases, was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為第 #5200 宗個案患者的家人，退休人士，無外遊紀錄， 10 月 5 日開始發燒，同日及 10 月 8 日就其他症症向將軍澳寶盈花園莊錦安醫生求診，10 月 11 日因發燒、咳嗽及神智欠佳到將軍澳醫院急症室求醫並留院接受治療。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5200, a retired person with no recent travel history. He developed fever on October 5, and visited the clinic of Dr Chong Kam On, Bauhinia Garden, Tseung Kwan O on October 5 and 8. He visited the accident & emergency department at Tseung Kwan O Hospital upon developing fever, coughs, and deliriousness, and was admitted for treatment.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 11 日乘搭 QR818 航班由法國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from France by flight QR818 on October 11, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 1 日乘搭 CX906 航班由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight CX906 on October 1, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者在太古城中心一期擔任文職，最後上班日期為 10 月 9 日。他無外遊紀錄， 10 月 10 日開始發燒，並於 11 日到基督教聯合醫院急症室求醫，翌日遞交深喉唾液樣本後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a clerk at Cityplaza One, Tai Koo Shing, and last attended work on October 9. He has no recent travel history and developed fever on October 10. He visited the accident & emergency department at United Christian Hospital on October 11, and the deep throat saliva sample he turned in next day tested positive for the virus.

detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5195, an employee at IFC Apple Store, with no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on October 6.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者屬 China Secret 群組，曾出席港威酒店聚會，從檢疫中心送院。他無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient belongs to the China Secret cluster and had been to the Gateway Hotel gathering. He was hospitalised from quarantine centre, with no recent travel history and having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 8 日乘搭 AI314 航班由印度抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrives in Hong Kong from India by flight AI314 on October 8, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者與第 #5211 宗個案患者一同於 10 月 13 日由法國抵港，沒有病徵。

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 13 日由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on Oct 13 and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為香港管弦樂團的低音單簧管樂手，10 月 9 及 10 日曾參與在香港文化中心音樂廳的演出。他無外遊紀錄，10 月 11 日發燒，翌日分別到仁安醫院求醫確診。
detail_en: The patient is a bass clarinet player in the Hong Kong Philharmonic Orchestra and participated in a performance at the Hong Kong Cultural Centre on Oct 9 and Oct 10. He has no recent travel history, developed a fever on Oct 11, and was diagnosed in Union Hospital the following day.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，10 月 4 日出現症狀，為家居密切接觸者。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on Oct 4, and is a close contact of a previous case whom she resided with.

detail_zh: 患者為商人，在尖沙咀好時中心工作，因要做小手術，10 月 12 日在仁安醫院接受測試，結果呈陽性。患者曾於 10 月 10 日內與妻子和 2 名朋友到置地廣場的日本餐廳 ZUMA 用膳， 10 月 1 日與 5、6人 在家吃飯，及於 10 月 9 日曾到九龍木球會比賽，比賽時雖無戴口罩，但球手會逐個入場，無互相接觸。他無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a businessman working at Earnings Limited, Tsim Sha Tsui, and tested positive at Union Hospital where he was scheduled to undergo a minor operation. He dined at ZUMA, Landmark with his wife and two friends on October 10, had a meal gathering at home with 5 to 6 others, and competed at the Kowloon Cricket Club. While he did not wear a mask during the competition, the players entered the cricket field individually without close contact. He has no recent travel history and exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵，第二個樣本確診。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on October 3, having exhibited no symptoms, and the second sample she turned in tested positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日由尼泊爾抵港，10 月 9 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on October 3 and developed symptoms on October 9.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者

detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and is a close contact of a patient. She developed symptoms on October 12 and was hospitalised from quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者與第 #5203 宗個案患者一同於 10 月 13 日由法國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from France along with patieht #5203 on October 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 3 日經土耳其由馬耳他抵港，10 月 12 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Turkey via Malta on October 3 and developed symptoms on October 12.

detail_zh: 患者為香港心理衞生會李鄭屋宿舍的社工，負責輔導工作，平日多在辦公室，辦公室旁邊有一間宿舍，住有 41 名院友，院友有需要時會到辦公室接受輔導。他於 10 月 11 日曾去土瓜灣中國基督教樂泉堂教堂參加崇拜，早上參加 8 人小組、下午參加 4 人小組，參與者均有佩戴口罩，同日與 3 名朋友在高山劇場「康姨小廚」午膳；10 月 12 日曾接院友一同在沙田租單車，踩往大埔，其間有戴口罩，午膳時曾與一名同事在沙田新城市廣場大家樂食飯，翌日發燒。潛伏期內患者則於 10 月 2 日，與一位友人到過景林邨一個室外運動場打籃球，及於 10 月 4 日與一位友人去將軍澳泳池游泳，亦有去學結他。
detail_en: The patient is a social worker at the Lei Cheng Uk Hostel of  Mental Health Association of Hong Kong who mainly provides counselling services at his office for the 41 residents at the adjoining hostel. He attended a church service at EFCC Joy Church, To Kwa Wan on October 11, taking part in an 8-person and a 4-person cell groups in the morning and afternoon respectively, with all attendees wearing masks. On the same day he had lunch at Madam Hong Restaurant, Ko  Shan Theatre with three other friends. On October 12 he led a group of hostel residents to bike from Shatin to Taipo with masks on, had lunch with a colleague at Café de Coral, New Town Plaza, Shatin, and developed fever on next day. During the incubation period he played basketball at an outdoor basketball court in King Lam Estate with a friend on October 2, went swimming at Tseung Kwan O Swimming Pool with a friend on October 4, and took guitar lessons.

detail_zh: 患者為駐港領事館人員， 10 月 15 日乘搭 AI314 由印度抵港，出發前在當地檢測結果呈陰性，抵港後向衞生防護中心人員提供其為身分證明，獲豁免檢疫，離開機場後隨即由領事館安排專車送返位於薄扶林花園第 6 座居所。衞生防護中心同日知悉其檢測結果呈初步陽性，立即將他送往公立醫院接受隔離治療，及後發現患者並非屬於可獲豁免強制檢疫的級別。患者抵達居所後一直獨留在居所，沒有外出，一直沒出現病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a member of a consulate in Hong Kong and arrived in Hong Kong from India by flight AI314 on October 15. His test result was negative prior to his departure and after arrival in Hong Kong he provided his identity certificate to CHP staff and was exempt from quarantine. After leaving the airport, the consulate arranged a private vehicle for him to return to his residence in Pokfulam Garden, Block 6. On the same day, the CHP learned that his test result was initially positive and immediately sent him to a public hospital for quarantine and treatment. The CHP later also discovered that the patient was not exempt from compulsory quarantine. After arriving at his residence, the patient stayed alone in his home, did not go out, and has no exhibited any symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者在港島東中心從事文職，10 月 16 日開始發冷發燒，18 日出現上呼吸道病徵及發燒症狀，同日到西灣河愛蝶灣鍾緯略醫生診所求診。醫生覺得患者病徵不像感染武漢肺炎，建議患者如擔心可去做測試。患者由丈夫駕車至油麻地梁顯利臨時檢測中心進行檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient works as a clerk at One Island East and developed chills and fever on October 16. She developed respitory symptoms and fever on October 18 and visited the clinic of Dr. Chung King Lueh at Aldrich Bay, Sai Wan Ho. The private practitioner recommended that the patient can undertake the coronavirus test in spite of the unlikeliness. Her husband drove her to the temporary testing centre at Henry G Leong Yaumatei Community Centre and she tested positive.

detail_zh: 患者無業，9 月 5 至 16 日曾到意大利及瑞士，9 月 16 日回港後，家居檢疫至 9 月 29 日，其間兩次接受病毒檢測均呈陰性。10 月 9 日曾有低燒，自行買藥服用後自覺已痊癒；10 月 19 日失去味覺，到屯門恆福花園司徒惠強醫生診所求診及留樣本，其後確診。患者平日每周有兩、三日到屯門新墟街市買餸；每晚會在住所樓下跑步往東涌碼頭，跑步期間有時沒戴口罩。她在傳染期內曾光顧食肆：10 月 11 日到東涌東匯城「八月花」，10 月 17 日到屯門海趣坊「意樂餐廳」，10 月 20 日到屯門青海圍「東哥點心火鍋第六分店」，10 月 21 日到東涌逸東商場「譚仔三哥米線」，另亦在 10 月 20 日在屯門新墟街市附近做腳部按摩。
detail_en: The patient is unemployed and travelled to Italy and Switzerland from September 5 to 16. She was under home quarantine since her return on September 16 until September 29, with two samples testing negative. She developed a mild fever on October 9 and self-diagnosed recovery. On October 19 she lost her sense of testing, and visited the clinic of Dr. Szeto Wai Keung at Hanford Garden and turned in a sample which tested positive. The patient buys grocery at San Hui Market, Tuen Mun two to three times a week, and jogs to Tung Chung Ferry Pier from her residence every night, sometimes without a mask. The restaurants she visited during incubation period are namely Jasmine, Citygate Tung Chung on October 11; Cafe de Itamomo, Ocean Walk Tuen Mun on October 17; Dong Gor Dim Sum and Hotpot Branch VI, Tsing Hoi Circuit Tuen Mun on October 20; and TamJai SamGor MiXian at Yat Tung Shopping Centre on October 21. She also had foot massage near San Hui Market on October 20.

detail_zh: 患者於鰂魚涌南豐新村 9 座與家人同住，在旺角豉油街萬利商業大廈工作，10 月 21 日不適翌日求醫，檢測樣本呈陽性。患者於 10 月 10 至 12 日曾與數名同事，在竹篙灣第二期檢疫中心沙井進行防水工程；14 至 16 日則曾到畢架山帝景峰工地工作，工作期間並非全程戴口罩。
detail_en: The patient resides with his family at Block 9, Nan Fung Sun Chuen, and works at Manly Commercial Building, Mong Kok. He developed illness on October 21 and sought medical examination next day, with his sample testing positive. He and several colleagues carried out waterproofing work for manholes at Penny's Bay Quarantine Centre Phase 2 from October 10 to 12; and at Dynasty Heights, Beacon Hill from October 14 to 16. He occasionally did not wear a mask during work.

detail_zh: 患者為第 #5312 宗個案患者的同事，於上環兆英商業大廈任文職，最後一日上班日期為 10 月 21 日。他無外遊紀錄， 10 月 20 日出現喉嚨痛，10 月 21 日向私家醫生馮國山求診，10 月 22 日到將軍澳（寶寧路）普通科門診診所求醫，翌日遞交深喉唾液樣本。
detail_en: The patient is the colleague of patient #5312, has no recent travel history and developed sore throat on October 20. He visited a private practitioner (Fung Kwok Shan Doctors) on October 21 and Tseung Kwan O (Po Ning Road) General Out-patient Clinic on October 22, and turned in a deep throat saliva sample next day. He works as a clerk at Siu Ying Commercial Building, Sheung Wan, and last attended work on October 21.

detail_en: The patient is the colleague of patient #5293, resides in Lok Chee Lau, Lok Man Sun Chuen, To Kwa Wan, and has no recent travel history. She goes to work in Siu Ying Commercial Building, 153 Queen's Road Central, Sheung Wan and her last day at work was Oct 23. She developed symptoms on Oct 22.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 16 日乘搭 PR300 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on Oct 16 aboard flight PR300 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月15 日乘搭 AI314 由印度抵港，10 月 28 日第二次驗測後確診，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on Oct 15 aboard flight AI314, tested positive on the second test on Oct 28, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為第 #5373 宗個案患者的丈夫， 10 月 19 日乘搭 QR881 經多哈由巴基斯坦抵港，10 月 27 日出現咳嗽症狀，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient is the husband of patient #5373,  arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Doha on Oct 19 aboard flight QR881, developed a cough on Oct 27, and was subsequently diagnosed positive.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 19 日乘搭 QR881 經多哈由巴基斯坦抵港，10 月 28 日檢測後確診，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Doha on Oct 19 aboard flight QR881, was diagnosed during testing on Oct 28, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 26  日與家人 ( 第 #5320 宗個案患者 ) 乘搭 AI1316 由印度抵港，因有家人為早前確診個案需接受檢疫，於檢疫中心確診，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India with a family member (patient #5320) on Oct 26 aboard flight AI1316. Due to a family member being diagnosed positive previously, the patient went under quarantine and was diagnosed during the quarantine period. He has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 26  日與家人 ( 第 #5319 宗個案患者 ) 乘搭 AI1316 由印度抵港，因有家人為早前確診個案需接受檢疫，於檢疫中心確診，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India with a family member (patient #5319) on Oct 26 aboard flight AI1316. Due to a family member being diagnosed positive previously, the patient went under quarantine and was diagnosed during the quarantine period. She has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者居於北角清華街 10 至 16 號，平日會坐公司車上班，於上環信德中心西座從事文職工作。患者最後上班日期為 10 月 29 日，27 日起開始感到疲倦，其公司共四十多人，有定期為員工安排檢測，10 月 9 日及 28 日均曾進行檢測，患者於 28 日檢測後確診，平常在公司吃飯後有時會在茶水間嗽口。患者於 10 月 23 日晚與朋友在港灣道體育館打羽毛球，24 日曾與朋友到柏架山行山，25 日與一名朋友到過畢架山行山，及後在蘇屋邨一茶餐廳用膳，28 日曾到啟業邨德源極上串王大排檔用餐。患者於打羽毛球及行山期間，大部分時間無佩戴口罩。衞生防護中心表示患者於 9 月底至 10 月初曾到深圳，並於 10 月 6 日經深圳灣口岸以豁免人士身分回港。
detail_en: The patient lives at 10-16 Ching Wah Street, North Point, and goes to work by company-arranged shuttles at West Tower, Shun Tak Centre, Sheung Wan. He last attended work on October 29 and developed fatigue on October 27. His company arranges regular coronavirus testing for the over 40 employees, the last ones being on October 9 and 28. He was diagnosed positive after the test on October 28. He occasionally rinses his mouth at the pantry at his office after meal. On October 23 he played badminton with his friends at Harbour Road Sports Centre. On October 24 he hiked with his friends on Mount Parker, and on October 25 with a friend on Beacon Hill and dined at a cha chaan teng at So Uk Estate. On October 28 he dined at Kai Yip Shopping Centre Cooked Food Stall. He did not wear a mask most of the time when he played badminton and hiked. CHP stated that the patient was in Shenzhen between late September and early October, and returned to Hong Kong on October 6 via Shenzhen Bay Port as an exempted person.

detail_zh: 患者為中國籍待遺返人士，來自貴州，8 月中旬在珠海經水路偷渡來港，之後留港從事性工作賺錢。10 月 28 日於警方掃黃行動中，涉嫌非法入境被捕。患者其後被帶到旺角警署。10 月 30 日被轉送到青山灣入境事務中心，逼留數小時後轉送馬頭角羈留中心，同日開始喉嚨痛。患者曾於大圍積存街 22 號一單位接客，其後因業主收樓，轉往旺角東方泛達酒店繼續接客。
detail_en: The patient is of Chinese nationality awaiting deportation. She is originally from Guizhou, and entered Hong Kong by sea through unofficial means from Zhuhai in mid-August, and stayed afterwards to earn income through sex work. She was arrested by police during an operation on October 28 on suspicion of illegal entrance into Hong Kong. She was later transferred to Mong Kok Police Station. On October 30 she was transferred to Castle Peak Bay Immigration Centre. After staying there for a few hours, she was transferred to Ma Tau Kok Detention Centre. She started developing a sore throat on the same day. The patient was meeting clients at 22 Chik Chuen, Tai Wai, and moved to Oriental Lander Hotel, Tong Mi Road, Mong Kok to meet clients due to the owner of the Tai Wai apartment repossessing the flat.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，居大埔圍頭村，在黃竹坑香葉道 1 號工作，平日乘家人私家車上班，最後一日上班日期為 10 月 28 日。她與 7 名朋友（包括第 #5336 宗個案患者）於 10 月 25 至 27 日入住梅窩銀礦灣海景渡假樂園 Staycation，分 3 間房，其間曾在酒店內一起燒烤，10 月 26 日在梅窩碼頭幾好餐廳及德仔記用膳，10 月 27 日在順興海鮮飯店午膳吃飯。10 月 27 日曾與第 #5337 及 第 #5338 宗個案患者吃飯，10 月 28 日開始發燒，同日向一名私家醫生求診並獲轉介至急症室求診。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and resides at Wai Tau Village, Tai Po, and works at 1 Heung Yip Road, Wong Chuk Hang. Her family members drive her to work and she last attended work on October 28. She and seven of her friends (including patient #5336) stayed at Seaview Holiday Resort, Silvermine Bay, Mui Wo, from October 25 to 27 for a staycation. They stayed in three rooms and had barbecues at the hotel. On Oct 26, she had meals at Ke Ho Restaurant and Tak Chai Kee Restaurant at Mui Wo Pier. On Oct 27, she had lunch at Shun Hing Seafood at Mui Wo Ferry Pier. She had shared meals with patients #5337 and #5338 on Oct 27. She developed fever on October 28, and was referred to accident & emergency department by a private practitioner on the same day.
