classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於廣福邨，為有線電視工程部員工，10 月 24 日起休假後便沒有上班，10 月 25 至 27 日與朋友（包括第 #5332 宗個案患者）入住海景渡假樂園 Staycation，分 3 間房，期間曾在酒店一起燒烤，10 月 26 日在梅窩碼頭幾好餐廳及德仔記用膳，10 月 27 日在順興海鮮飯店午膳吃飯。他無外遊紀錄，10 月 30 日出現咳嗽及流鼻水症狀，31 日曾與 7 名工程部同事及一名兼職記者在粉嶺下輋路一朋友的家中吃火鍋，亦曾有其他聚會。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kwong Fuk Estate and is an engineering staff member at Cable TV. He did not attend work since his leave of absence from October 24 onwards. From October 25 to 27 he and his friends (patient #5332 inclusive) stayed at Seaview Holiday Resort, Silvermine Bay, Mui Wo for staycation. They stayed in three rooms and had barbecues at the hotel. On Oct 26, he had meals at Ke Ho Restaurant and Tak Chai Kee Restaurant at Mui Wo Pier. On Oct 27, he had lunch at Shun Hing Seafood at Mui Wo Ferry Pier. He has no recent travel history. On October 30 he developed coughs and runny nose; on October 31 he had hotpot meal with seven other engineering staff colleagues and a part-time reporter at Ha Che Road, Fanling; and he attended other gatherings as well.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5332 宗個案患者的親戚，同住圍頭村，惟屬另一間屋，10 月 27 日曾與第 #5332 及 第#5338 宗個案患者吃飯。他就讀於粉嶺基督教香港信義會心誠中學，10 月 30 日曾回校上課，活動期間未有除下口罩，放學後曾與朋友進餐；10 月 29 日與十多名朋友，無戴口罩在聯和墟打籃球。他於 10 月31 日與家人拜山，同日出現咳嗽症狀，後知有親戚確診後到急症室求醫，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a relative of patient #5332 who resides at another house also in Wai Tau Village. They had a meal together on October 27 along with patient #5338. He studies at Fanling Lutheran Secondary School and attended class on October 30. He did not take off his mask during activities and he had meals with friends after school. On October 29, he and more than ten other friends played basketball at Luen Wo Market without wearing masks. He visited graves to pay respects along with his family on October 31 and developed coughs on the same day. He sought medical examination upon knowledge of his relative's diagnosis, and was later diagnosed positive.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，10 月 27 日曾與第 #5332 及 #5337 宗個案患者吃飯，10 月 30 日開始喉嚨痛，11 月 1 日經衛生防護中心追蹤後送往檢疫中心，及後確診。其家人（第 #5348 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, and on October 27 he dined with patients #5332 and #5337. He developed sore throat on October 30, and was transferred to quarantine centre upon contact tracing by CHP on November 1, thereafter being diagnosed positive for the virus. His family member (patient #5348) has also tested positive.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 1 日由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the USA on November 1, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為空中服務員，11 月 1 日乘搭 BA27 由英國抵港，潛伏期曾到過美國及以色列，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a flight attendent arriving in Hong Kong from the UK by flight BA27 on November 1. She travelled to the USA and Israel during incubation period, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為空中服務員，11 月 1 日乘搭 BA27 由英國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a flight attendent arriving in Hong Kong from the UK by flight BA27 on November 1, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5332 宗個案患者的家人，香港專業教育學院 （IVE） 青衣分校學生，最後上課日為 10 月 30 日，回校上課期間有佩戴口罩。他無外遊紀錄，11 月 1 日因發燒送院。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5332 and studies at Hong Kong Institute of Vocational Education (Tsing Yi Campus). He last attended class on October 30 with a mask on. He has no recent travel history and was hospitalised on November 1 upon developing fever.

detail_zh: 患者獨居於銅鑼灣人和悅大廈，在中環花園道 3 號從事文職工作，10 月 29 日最後一日上班，10 月 30 日發病，翌日到養和醫院求診及確診。10 月 17 日曾與約 20 名朋友在黃竹坑運動場踢足球，10 月 25 日在鴨脷洲深灣軒運動場與數名朋友打籃球，同日曾到雲咸街 Bar De Luxe 與朋友飲酒，10 月 21 及 28 日曾到朋友位於中環中心的辦公室與約 10 人玩啤牌。
detail_en: The patient resides on his own at Yan Wo Yuet Building, Causeway Bay, and works as a clerk at 3 Garden Road, Central, last attending work on October 29. He developed symptoms on October 30, sought medical examination at Hong Kong Sanatorium & Hospital, and diagnosed positive for the virus, On October 17 he played football at Aberdeen Sports Ground, Wong Chuk Hang with about 20 other friends. On October 25 he played basketball at the basketball court at Sham Wan Towers, Ap Lei Chau with several other friends, and visited Bar De Luxe, Wyndham Street on the same day. On October 21 and 28 he played poker card with around 10 other friends at the office of his friend at The Center.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，10 月 22 日乘搭 5J142 由菲律賓抵港，11 月 2 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from he Philippines by flight 5J142 on October 22. She developed symptoms on November 2.

detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight CX796, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 25 至 27 日曾與第 #5332 宗個案患者一起去梅窩 Staycation 及聚餐，無外遊紀錄，10 月 31 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient went on the Mui Wo staycation and group meals with patient #5332 from October 25 to 27, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on October 31.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5338 宗個案患者的家人，是一名家庭主婦，無外遊紀錄，11 月 2 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #533 a. She is a housewife, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on November 2.

detail_zh: 患者為女傭，由印度抵港，11 月 3 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from India, and developed symptoms on November 3.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，11 月 3 日乘搭 PR300 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Bangkok by flight KL847 after connecting flights from Brazil and Amsterday, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者任職貨機維修工作，與家人同住錦田水流田村。最後上班日期為 10 月 27 日早上 ( 夜更 ) ，工作有需要接觸貨機機組人員，10 月 30 日開始喉嚨痛。患者 10 月 28 日曾帶兒子到九龍灣公園足球場參加培訓班，同日亦到過九龍灣 Mega Box Pepper Lunch 及玩具反斗城。10 月 29 日曾到馬鞍山恆康街足球場。10 月 31 日曾到天水圍天瑞邨足球場、石門賽馬會傑志中心及元朗 448 農莊，但沒隨同家人於農莊留宿。11 月 4 日曾到摩士公園足球場。患者帶同兒子到足球場期間有佩戴口罩，只坐場邊沒參與足球運動。其兩名兒子分別就讀天水圍靈愛小學及錦田聖公會聖約瑟堂幼稚園。
detail_en: The patient is a cargo aircraft maintenace worker and lives with his family in Shui Lau Tin Tsuen. His last day at work was the morning of Oct 27 at the end of his night shift. His work required him to interact with other cargo aircraft crew members. On Oct 30, he developed a sore throat. On Oct 28, he had brought his son to Kowloon Bay Park Football Field to attend a training course and also visited Mega Box Pepper Lunch and Toys R Us in Kowloon Bay. On Oct 29, he had been to the football field on Hang Hong St in Ma On Shan.  On Oct 31, he had been to the football field in Tin Shui Estate, Tin Shui Wai, the Jockey Club Kitchee Centre in Shek Mun, and 448 Farm in Yuen Long. He did not stay with his family members at the farmstay. On Nov 4, he visited the football field in Morse Park. The patient wore a mask when he brought his son to the football field and they only sat on the sidelines without participating in football. His other two sons study in S K H Tin Shui Wai Ling Oi Primary School in Tin Shui Wai and SKH St.Joseph's Church Kindergarten on Kam Sheung Road.

detail_zh: 患者與家人居與大埔廣福邨廣平樓，於崇德街 8 號 A Inn Club 工作，負責接待客人，不需要煮食，最後上班日期為 10 月 29 日。10 月 31 日開始有輕微咳嗽，數天後覺得已好轉。11  月 3 日因仍有擔心到王少清母嬰健康院取樣本瓶，5 日交回樣本。患者 11 月 4 日曾與一名朋友到翠和里 1 號的德美壽司用餐。
detail_en: The patient lives at Kwong Ping House, Kwong Fuk Estate, Tai Po with his family, and works at Inn Club, 8A Shung Tak Street. He serves customers and is not in charge of cooking, and he last attended work on October 29. On October 31 he developed mild coughs, and felt it improved after several days. On November 3 he obtained a sample bottle from Wong Siu Ching Family Medicine Centre out of concern, and returned a sample on November 5. On November 4 he and another friend dined at Sushi Tokumi, 1 Chui Wo Lane.

detail_zh: 患者居於愉景灣倚濤軒。在中環冠君大廈任文職，最後上班日為 10 月 16 日。10 月 19日發燒，之後與家人均一直無外出，她與丈夫沒有上班，其兩名子女亦沒上學近 3 星期。患者 11 月 5 日到私家診所取樣本瓶做檢測，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides in Crestmont Villa, Discovery Bay and is employd in Champion Tower, Central. Her last day at work was Oct 16. She started having a fever on Oct 19 and since then has not gone out with her family. She and her husband did not go to work and her two children have not been to school for nearly three weeks. On Nov 5, she went to a private clinic to obtain a sample bottle for testing and was later diagnosed positive.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5317 宗個案患者的妻子，居於八鄉梁屋村翠苑，沒有病徵，今年 7 月由巴基斯坦回港，當時曾在駿洋邨檢疫，兩次新冠病毒檢測呈陰性。她潛伏期主要留在家中，間中會到元朗一濕街市買菜。報稱在丈夫 10 月 19 日返港後未曾與其接觸，在丈夫入院後，與兩名孩子於 11 月 5 日到博愛醫院急症室並採樣，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient is the wife of patient #5317, resides in Green Villa, Leung Uk Tsuen, and has exhibited no symptoms. She returned to Hong Kong from Pakistan in July and had undergone quarantine in Chun Yeung Estate as well as testing negative twice for the novel coronavirus. During the incubation period, she was mainly at home. She went out sometimes to buy groceries in a wet market in Yuen Long. It has been reported that she no contact with her husband since he returned to Hong Kong on Oct 19. After her husband was hospitalized, she went with her two children to Pok Oi Hospital Accident and Emergency Department on Nov 5 to leave samples and was later diagnosed positive.

detail_en: The patient is the husband of patient #5382, resides at Hing Wo House, Po Nga Court, Tai Po, and works as a clerk at 108 Gloucester Road, Wan Chai, last attending work on November 6. The patient developed coughs on October 28, and visited Baptist Hospital on November 4 upon experiencing shortness of breath, testing positive for the virus. He dined at Tristar Kitchen, Shatin New Town Plaza on November 6.

detail_zh: 患者為退休人士，居於葵盛西邨第 9 座，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。11 月 9 日因自身健康問題到仁濟醫院，入院篩查時發現確診，其病毒量低，抗體測試結果為陽性，代表可能較早前已感染。他平常會到荃灣公園、登打士街公園獨坐，亦曾光顧旺角金苑酒家。
detail_en: The patient is a retired person residing at Block 9, Kwai Shing West Estate, with no recent travel history, and exhibited no symptoms. On November 9 he visited Yan Chai Hospital upon personal health concerns, and tested positive at screening upon admission. He has a low viral load and positive result for antibodies, meaning that he was likely infected earlier on. He usually sits on his own at Tsuen Wan Park and Dundas Street Sitting Out Area, and dined at Gold Garden Restaurant, Mongkok.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，居於屯門明偉大廈，為浸會大學學生，最後一日上課為 11 月 3 日，返校其間有佩戴口罩。她 11 月 4 至 5 日與 5 名朋友到北角凱悅尚萃酒店 Staycation，10 月 30 至 31 日與 10 多名朋友到旺角帝京酒店 Staycation，亦曾到多區場館做運動，包括深水埗體育館、長沙灣保安道體育館、順利邨體育館、黃竹坑 One Island South 一間跆拳道青道館以及炮台山六合商業大廈一間跆拳道館。10 月 8 日曾到妙法齋吃午餐；11 月 4 日到屯門置樂「美集」做美容；11 月 5 日到旺角中心一間牙醫診所，當時無不適，但離開後乘車期間覺得不適，前往求醫。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, resides at Ming Wai Building, Tuen Mun, and is a student at Hong Kong Baptist University. She last attended classes on November 3 and wore a mask throughout the day. She had staycations with five other friends at Hyatt Centric Victoria Harbour, North Point from November 4 to 5, and  with more than 10 other friends at Royal Plaza Hotel, Mong Kok from October 30 to 31. She also exercised at facilities across different districts, including Sham Shui Po Sports Ground; Po On Road Sports Centre, Cheung Sha Wan; Shun Lee Tsuen Sports Centre; Cheung Do Kwan School, One Island South, Wong Chuk Hang; and a Taekwondo School at Concord Commercial Building, Fortress Hill. She had lunch at Miu Fat Chai on October 8; had facial at People Beauty, Chi Lok Fa Yuen, Tuen Mun on November 4; and a dental clinic at Argyle Centre on November 5 when she experienced illness upon departure and sought medical examination.

detail_zh: 患者與家人居住在荃灣全．城匯，在沙田石門偉達中心上班，任職項目經理。患者平日常到石門京瑞廣場幾間食肆用午膳，包括狀元橋米線、麗島小廚及台豐台灣美食；晚上常到荃新天地米線陣及乜記餐室用膳；曾到如心海景酒店的如粵滬中菜廳用膳；11 月 5 日曾到西貢 Beach Club 與朋友飲酒；另亦曾光顧石門永興食堂。他無外遊紀錄，11 月 6 日出現喉嚨痛及流鼻水症狀。其家人（第 #5444 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides with his family in PARC CITY, Tsuen Wan and works in Grandtech Centre, Sha Tin as a project manager. He usually has lunch at several restaurants at Kings Wing Plaza, including The Champion, Laguna Phuket Kitchin, and Tai Fung Taiwanese Delicacy. He had dinners at Mixian Sense and What Cafe at Citywalk, Tsuen Wan, and Ru Chinese Restaurant, L'Hotel Nina. On November 5 he had alcoholic drinks with friends at Beach Club, and he also visited Wing Hing Eatery And Cart Noodle, Shek Mun. He has no recent travel history and developed sore throat and runny nose on November 6. His family member (patient #5444) has also been diagnosed positive.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal and developed symptoms in Oct. (On Nov 12, the CHP updated the patient's onset date.)

detail_zh: 患者為尼泊爾駐港領事館職員，獲豁免檢疫人士，11 月 9 日出現症狀。11 月 10 日由尼泊爾抵港，同日返抵紅磡都會軒 1 座住所後被通知確診，於聯合醫院留醫。入院時沒有病徵，情況穩定，入院後病毒檢測結果呈陽性，但病毒量偏低；驗血報告顯示患者有抗體，符合出院標準，故獲安排 11 月 12 日出院。
detail_en: The patient is a staff member at Consulate General of Nepal in Hong Kong, was exempted from quarantine, and developed symptoms on Nov 9. She arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on Nov 10, and returned to her residence at Block 1, The Metropolis Residence in Hung Hom where she was later notified of her positive diagnosis. She was admitted to United Christian Hospital for treatment. She exhibited no symptoms upon admission and her condition was stable. During hospitalization, her virus test was positive, however the virus load was low. The patient's blood test report showed the presence of antibodies and her condition met the discharge criteria. She was scheduled to be discharged from hospital on Nov 12.

He usually hands over his shift at Golden Computer Arcade and Lai Kok Estate, and has few activities outsides work. He developed coughs on November 8.

detail_zh: 患者為的士司機，為運輸署轉介個案，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。患者已退休一段時間，正準備再擔任的士司機而領取車牌及接受檢測，故未有接觸任何乘客。
detail_en: The patient is a taxi driver and his case is referred from Transport Department. He has no recent travel history and exhibited no symptoms. He retired for a while and was preparing to work as a taxi driver again, so he took a test while registering for his driving license. Therefore he has no contact with any passenger.

detail_zh: 患者任職保母車及復康巴士司機，最後上班日期為 11 月 10 日，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。工作駕駛路線主要為啟田往聯合醫院，與及柴灣興華邨至小西灣綜合大樓 ( 東區醫院線 )。患者家住火炭，潛伏期及傳染期均有駕駛保母車接載學生，涉及學校包括保良局蕭漢森小學，及保良局張心瑜幼稚園。
detail_en: The patient is a nanny van and rehab bus driver, and last attended work on November 10. He has no recent travel history and exhibited no symptoms. He is mainly responsible for routes between Kai Tin Estate and United Christian Hospital, and between Hing Wah Estate and Siu Sai Wan Complex (Pamela Youde Nethersole Eastern Hospital route). He lives in Fo Tan and drove a nanny van during both incubation and infectious periods for students of P.L.K. Siu Hon Sum Primary School and PLK Fiona Cheung Sum Yu Kindergarten.

detail_zh: 患者為兼職早班的士司機，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵，為運輸署轉介個案，最後上班日期為 11 月 9 日。11 月 7 日曾與家人往百樂潮州酒樓用膳，亦曾與同事聚餐。
detail_en: The patient is a part-time early shift taxi driver, with no recent travel history, and exhibited no symptoms. His case is referred from Transport Department. He last attended work on November 9. On November 7 he and his family dined at Pak Loh Chiu Chow Restaurant, Mong Kok, and he also had meal gathering with colleagues.

detail_zh: 患者逢一、三及五任兼職的士司機，為運輸署轉介個案，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。平日在大圍交更，會到上水天光墟買菜，在第 6 次接受運輸署安排的定期測試時確診，上次測試日期為 10 月 30 日。
detail_en: The patient is a part-time taxi driver working on Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays, and his case is referred from Transport Department. He has no recent travel history and exhibited no symptoms. He usually hands over his shift at Tai Wai, and buys grocery at Sheung Shui Tin Kwong (Dawn) Flea Market. He tested positive at the 6th round of Transport Department routine testing, and he last tested on October 30.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 9 日乘搭 CX252 由英國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UK on Nov 9 aboard flight CX252 and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於錦田水流田村，無外遊紀錄，為早前確診患者的家人，多名親戚曾到患者家中作客。他 11 月 6 日入住檢疫中心，11 月 10 日發燒。
detail_en: The patient resides in Shui Lau Tin Tsuen, has no recent travel history, and is the family member of a previously diagnosed patient. Many relatives had recently visited the patient's home. He was admitted to the quarantine centre on Nov 6 and developd a fever on Nov 10.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月10 日乘搭 RA409 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on Nov 10 aboard flight RA409 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月10 日乘搭 RA409 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on Nov 10 aboard flight RA409 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為機師，11 月 10 日由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a pilot, arrived in Hong Kong from the US on Nov 10, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為機師，11 月 10 日由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a pilot, arrived in Hong Kong from the US on Nov 10, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者居於青龍頭豪景花園 8 座，為香港寬頻銷售員，在九龍灣國際展貿中心上班，最後上班日期為 11 月 11 日。他無外遊紀錄，11 月 9 日不適，看醫生後確診，他曾到大角咀塘尾道金沙餐廳、太子元朗冰室、屯門啟豐商場小桃園、九龍灣祥和食堂及信和食堂、光輝圍雲貴軒及九龍灣台灣麵，10 月 26 日到尖沙咀 The ONE「譽宴．星海」出席一個有 300 人的婚宴；11 月 7 日與親戚聚會。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 8, Hong Kong Garden, Tsing Lung Tau, and is a salesperson for Hong Kong Broadband Network working at Kowloon Bay International Trade & Exhibition Centre. He last attended work on November 11. He has no recent travel history, developed illness on November 9, and was diagnosed by a private practitioner. He dined at Golden Sand Restaurant, Tong Mei Road, Tai Kok Tsui; Yuen Long Bistro, Prince Edward; a restaurant (小桃園) at Richland Garden, Tuen Mun; two canteens (祥和食堂 and 信和食堂) at Kowloon Bay; The Vermicelli House, Kwong Fai Circuit; and Taiwan Kitchen, Kowloon Bay. On October 26 he attended a wedding banquet at U-Banquet The Starview, The ONE attended by 300 people. On November 7 he had a gathering with his relatives.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月10 日乘搭 QR818 由瑞典經多哈抵港，10 月 27 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Sweden via Doha on Nov 10 aboard flight QR818 and developed symptoms on Oct 27.

detail_zh: 患者為貨機機師，11 月 11 日由德國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a cargo aircraft pilot, arrived in Hong Kong from Germany on Nov 11, and has no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，11 月 8 日乘搭 CX796 由印尼抵港，沒有病徵，由檢疫中心送院。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia on Nov 8 aboard flight CX796, has exhibited no symptoms, and was transferred to hospital from quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，11 月 8 日乘搭 CX796 由印尼抵港，沒有病徵，由檢疫中心送院。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia on Nov 8 aboard flight CX796, has exhibited no symptoms, and was transferred to hospital from quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者居於大埔中心 18 座，為沙田威爾斯親王醫院李炳醫學圖書館的中大職員，最後上班日期為 11 月 9 日。他 11 月 7 日發燒、咳嗽、流鼻水和喉嚨痛症狀，9 日在中文大學保健處求診，其後確診。他平日會去跑步，曾到過大埔運動場，與朋友到九龍坑山行山；亦曾到多間餐廳吃飯，包括大埔昌運中心瑞峰軒酒樓、昌運中心咪走雞燒味至尊小廚，及大埔廣場爭鮮。
detail_en: The patient resides in Block 18 of Tai Po Centre and is a staff member at Li Ping Medical Library (The Chinese University of Hong Kong) at Prince of Wales Hospital. His last day at work was Nov 9. He developed fever, cough, runny nose, and sore throat on Nov 7. On Nov 9, he had visited the University Health Centre at The Chinese University of Hong Kong for consultation and was later diagnosed. He goes jogging on the weekdays and had recently been to Tai Po Sports Ground. He had also been to Cloudy Hill for a hike with friends. He had been to many restaurants recently, including Julimount Restaurant in Fortune Plaza Arcade, Tai Po, 咪走雞燒味至尊小廚, also in Fortune Plaza Arcade, and Sushi Express in Tai Po Plaza.

detail_zh: 患者為退休人士，居於旺角新填地街德豐大廈，11 月 9 日開始發燒、咳嗽和流鼻水，10 日向油麻地賽馬會普通科門診診所求診，翌日遞交深喉唾液樣本。平日他會與朋友行山，包括由旺角行去坑口、西貢井欄樹等。11 月 8 日曾到大角咀浸信會做崇拜，其間有戴口罩。他亦曾到大角咀彩翠軒酒家飲茶，及到洋松街鴻昌茶餐廳吃飯。其家人及行山朋友（第 #5459 及 5457 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient is retired and resides in Tak Fung Building, Reclamation St, Mong Kok. On Nov 9, he developed fever, cough, and runny nose. On Nov 10, he visited Yau Ma Tei Jockey Club General Out-patient Clinic for consultation and submitted a deep throat saliva sample the next day. On weekdays, he goes hiking with friends, including from Mong Kok to Hang Hau, Tseng Lan Shue in Sai Kung, etc. On Nov 8, he had been to Tai Kok Tsui Baptist Church for worship, during which he wore a mask. He had also recently had dim sum in Jade Palace Chinese Restaurant, 70 Beech St, Tai Kok Tsui, and had a meal at Hong Chang Dim Sum Restaurant, Larch St, Tai Kok Tsui. His family member and hiking friend (patients #5459 and #5457) have also been diagnosed positive.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 11 日乘搭 LX138 航班由德國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Germany on Nov 11 aboard flight LX138 and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於太古城太湖閣，浸會大學體育系學生，最後回浸大上課日期為 10 月 23 日，自 11 月初到協恩中學實習，任教體育科，涉及中一、中三和中四 3 班共約 120 名學生，任教時師生均全程戴上口罩。她是第 #5398 宗個案患者的的密切接觸者，但沒有跟該女生一同參加酒店 Staycation，11 月 10 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides in Tai Woo Mansion, Tai Koo Shing, and is a student at the Department of Physical Education in Baptist University. The last time she attended class at Baptist University was Oct 23. She had been undertaking teaching practicum at Heep Yunn School since the beginning of November as a physical education teacher, interacting with approximately 120 students from Form 1, Form 3, and Form 4. Teachers and students wear masks throughout the teaching period. She is a close contact of patient #5398 but did not participate with her in the Staycation. She developed symptoms on Nov 10.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5409 宗個案患者的妻子，居於長沙灣海麗邨海暉樓，無外遊紀錄，11 月 6 日出現症狀，同日曾到海麗商場喜兆年酒家，另 11 月10 日曾到深水埗北河街街市。
detail_en: The patient is the wife of patient #5409 and resides in Hoi Lai Estate Hoi Fai House in Cheung Sha Wan. She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on Nov 6. On the same day she developd symptoms, she had been to a restaurant (喜兆年酒家) in Hoi Lai Shopping Centre. On Nov 10, she had been to Pei Ho Market in Sham Shui Po.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，10 月 31 日乘搭 CX796 航班由印尼抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia on Oct 31 aboard flight CX796 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者曾到立陶宛和白羅斯，11 月 12 日乘搭 TK070 經土耳其抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient visited Latvia and Belarus and returned to Hong Kong from Turkey by flight TK070 on November 12, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，與 2 名家人居於慈雲山慈康邨康潤樓，在佐敦莊士倫敦廣場擔任夜更保安，最後上班日期為 11 月 11 日。他曾於 11 月 6 日與 3 名親戚朋友在旺角金御酒家一同用膳。11 月 8 日出現症狀，11 月 10 日曾向私家醫生求醫，但沒有按醫生指示提交樣本作病毒檢測，翌日依然感到不適，遂到廣華醫院急症室求醫。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, and resides at Hong Yun House, Tsz Hong Estate, Tsz Wan Shan with two other family members. He works as a night-shift security guard at Chuang's London Plaza and last attended work on November 11. On November 6 he and other three relatives and friends dined at Majesty Chinese Restaurant, Mong Kok. On November 8 he developed symptoms, and on November 10 he visited a private practitioner, but did not turn in a sample for testing as instructed. He continued experiencing illness next day and visited the accident & emergency department at Kwong Wah Hospital.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者與丈夫居於大埔廣福邨廣仁樓，其丈夫曾與一名確診者行山。她無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，到大埔廣福邨臨時取樣中心參加檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kwong Yan House, Kwong Fuk Estate, Tai Po with her husband. Her husband went hiking with a previously diagnosed patient. She has no recent travel history, exhibited no symptoms, and tested positive at a temporary testing centre at Kwong Fuk Estate.

detail_zh: 患者曾到羅馬尼亞，11 月 12 日乘搭 QR818 經多哈抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient visited Romania and returned to Hong Kong by flight QR818 via Doha on November 12, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者曾到德國，11 月 12 日乘搭 QR818 經多哈抵港，翌日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient had recently been in Germany, arriving in Hong Kong on Nov 12 via Doha on flight QR818, and developed symptoms the following day.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 10 日由尼泊爾抵港，因同行者確診被送入檢疫中心，11 月 10 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on October 10, and was transferred to quarantine centre as his travel companion tested positive. He developed symptoms on November 10.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5399 宗個案患者的家人，居於荃灣全．城匯 7 座，在觀塘渣打銀行中心上班。她無外遊紀錄，11 月 7 日出現症狀，由檢疫中心送院。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5399 and resides at Tower 7, Parc City, and works at Standard Chartered Tower, Kwun Tong. She has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on November 7, and was hospitalised from quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者曾到立陶宛和白羅斯，11 月 6 日出現病徵，11 月 12 日乘搭 TK070 經土耳其抵港。
detail_en: The patient visited Latvia and Belarus, developed symptoms on November 6, and returned to Hong Kong from Turkey by flight TK070 on November 12.

detail_zh: 患者為一名裝修工人，與家人居於沙田新田圍邨盛圍樓，馬會跑馬地會所更衣室的裝修承建商的員工，最後上班日期為 11 月 9 日，於會所逗留其間曾到 2 樓及 5 樓檢查更衣室，期間有佩戴口罩。他無外遊紀錄，11 月 6 日出現發燒症狀，11 月 12 日向沙田新田圍邨商場的吳廣鴻醫生求診。10 月 24 日曾與朋友到過尖沙咀金馬倫道一間酒吧。
detail_en: The patient works as a renovator and resides at Shing Wai House, Sun Tin Wai Estate with his family. He is a worker for the contractor of the changing rooms at the Hong Kong Jockey Club Happy Valley Clubhouse, last attending work on November 9. He inspected the changing rooms on 2/F and 5/F with a mask on. He has no recent travel history and developed fever on November 6. On November 12 he visited the clinic of Dr. Ng Kwong Hung at Sun Tin Wai Shoping Centre, and on October 24 he went to a bar on Cameron Road, Tsim Sha Tsui.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，11 月 13 日乘搭 CX796 由印尼抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight CX796 on November 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，11 月 13 日乘搭 CX796 由印尼抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight CX796 on November 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為船員，11 月 13 日乘搭 TK070 由波蘭經土耳其抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor arriving in Hong Kong from Poland via Turkey by flight TK070 on November 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，11 月 13 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight CX906 on November 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為豁免檢疫人士，11 月 13 日乘搭 TK070 由匈牙利經土耳其抵港，確診前曾回到鴨脷洲南灣 9 座的住所，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is exempted from compulsory quarantine, arriving in Hong Kong from Hungary via Turkey by flight TK070 on November 13. Prior to diagnosing positive she returnd to her residence at Tower 9, Larvotto, Ap Lei Chau, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 13 日乘搭 EK384 由孟加拉經杜拜抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Bangladesh via Dubai by flight EK384 on November 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 13 日乘搭 KL847 由俄羅斯抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Russia by flight KL847 on November 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 11 日乘搭 EK384 由阿聯酋抵港，11 月 13 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UAE by flight EK384 on November 11, and developed symptoms on November 13.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5439 及 #5456 宗個案患者的家人，居於慈雲山慈康邨康潤樓，在鑽石山鳳德社區中心工作，最後上班日期是 11 月 11 日。她無外遊紀錄，11 月 11 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5439 and #5455, resides at Hong Yun House, Tsz Hong Estate, Tsz Wan Shan, and works at Fung Tak Estate Community Centre, last attending work on November 11. She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on November 11.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5439 及 #5455 宗個案患者的家人，居於慈雲山慈康邨康潤樓，在太子始創中心4樓的潮．悅酒樓工作。她無外遊紀錄，11 月 11 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5439 and #5455, resides at Hong Yun House, Tsz Hong Estate, Tsz Wan Shan, and works at Chiu Garden, 4/F Pioneer Centre, Prince Edward. She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on November 11.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5440 宗個案患者的家人，#5433 宗個案患者的朋友，居於大埔廣福邨廣仁樓，無外遊紀錄，11 月 11 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5440 and a friend of patient #5433, resides at Kwong Yan House, Kwong Fuk Estate, Tai Po. He has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on November 11.

detail_zh: 患者 10 月 31 日乘搭 TK070 航班由德國經土耳其抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Germany via Turkey by flight TK070 on October 31, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #5433 宗個案患者的家人，居於旺角德豐大廈，無外遊紀錄，11 月 11 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5433, resides at Tak Fung Building, Mong Kok, and has no recent travel history. She developed symptoms on November 11.

detail_zh:
患者為外傭，11 月 14 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港
，沒有病徵，由機場送院。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight CX906, having exhibited no symptoms. She was hospitalised from the airport.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 14 日乘搭 QR818 由巴基斯坦經多哈抵港，沒有病徵，由等候檢測結果中心送院。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Doha by flight QR818 on November 14, having exhibited no symptoms. He was hospitalised from the test waiting centre.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 14 日乘搭 EK384 由巴基斯坦經杜拜抵港，沒有病徵，由等候檢測結果中心送院。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Dubai by flight EK384 on November 14, having exhibited no symptoms. She was hospitalised from the test waiting centre.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 5 日乘搭 QR818 由西班牙經多哈抵港，在機場接受檢測時呈陰性反應，返回將軍澳南豐廣場 6 座住所接受強制檢疫；11 月 12 日出現症狀，到醫院求醫後確診。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Spain via Doha by flight QR818 on November 5, and tested negative for the virus at the airport. She was under compulsory quarantine at her residence at Block 6, Nan Fung Plaza, Tseung Kwan O. She developed symptoms on November 12 and tested positive during a medical examination at a hospital.

detail_zh: 患者為機組人員，乘搭 UP544 由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a flight crew member arriving in Hong Kong from the USA by flight UP544, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者沒有病徵，由孟加拉抵港，抵港後其深喉唾液樣本結果為陰性，故可到香港荃灣絲麗酒店接受強制檢疫，後來發現其漱口樣本初步陽性，送院後確診。
detail_en: The patient exhibited no symptoms and arrived in Hong Kong from Bangladesh. His deep throat saliva sample tested negative and he was under compulsory quarantine at Silka Tsuen Wan Hotel. His saliva sample was later found to test preliminarily positive, and he was hospitalised and thereafter diagnosed positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者 11 月 3 日由印度抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on November 3, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為 1 歳男童，沒有病徵，由尼泊爾抵港，由於他不適合接受深喉唾液測試，機場職員給他糞便樣本收集包；家人其後交回樣本到收集點，糞便樣本驗出病毒後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a one-year-old infant, having exhibited no symptoms, and arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal. His stool sample was turned in in lieu of deep throat saliva sample, which tested positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者為機組人員，11 月 15 日乘搭 TK070 由土耳其抵港，同日出現症狀。

detail_en: The patient is an aviation engineer arriving in Hong Kong from Germany via Dubai on a test flight for a new aircraft on November 15, with no passengers on board. He exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者居於元朗采葉庭 12 座，為工程管工，在荔枝角瓊林街陸佰中心上班，一週有兩、三天會到西環創業商場地盤工作，最近上班日期為 11 月 16 日。11 月 12 日開始喉嚨痛，當日曾向私家醫生求醫，醫生建議留樣本，但患者於 11 月 15 日自行到元朗檢測中心檢測，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tower 12, The Parcville, Yuen Long, and works as a construction foreman at Centre 600, King Lam Street, Lai Chee Kok. He works at a construction site at Chong Yip Shopping Centre, Sai Wan two to three days a week, last attending work on November 16. On November 12 he developed sore throat and visited a private practitioner on that day, who suggested that he turn in a sample. On November 15, he undertook a test at a community testing centre in Yuen Long and tested positive for the virus.

detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #5474, both of whom resides at Block 6, Kwai Shing West Estate. He works as a day-shift security guard at Chuang's London Plaza, and has no direct contact with the earlier-diagnosed night-shift security guard (patient #5439), possibly having been infected due to their sharing of the same changing room. He has no recent travel history and exhibited no symptoms.

He has no recent travel history and his social activities are usually limited to the vicinity of his residence. He previously had dim-sum meal at Lung Shun Hin Seafood Restaurant, Kwai Shing West Estate Shopping Centre.

He works from 9am to 8pm on weekdays and usually serves the Kowloon area, but he had dined at different places. On November 10 he developed mild coughs, and on November 16 he was admitted to Prince Wales Hospital upon developing asthma. He previously took a test designated for taxi drivers, and tested negative in October. His family member (patient #5492) later on tested positive as well.

She resides at 10 Cloud View Road, North Point, runs a clinic at Argyle Centre, Mong Kok, and also practises at Union Hospital Polyclinic (Ma On Shan). On November 23 she developed coughs, and undertook a test at a medical appointment on the same day. On November 24 she was on duty at Union Hospital Polyclinic (Ma On Shan) without informing the staff regarding her conditions. The other doctors and clinic staff had protective gears, face shields, and masks on.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者患有末期肺癌，8 月中起住在養和醫院 33 樓單人房，一直咳嗽和有痰，生前有 3 名家人常探訪。她自 11 月 25 日起發燒，翌日呼吸困難，等待檢測結果期間心臟病發，26 日離世，離世後被驗出確診。患者生前病毒量高，免疫力低，需聞氧，曾用霧化藥物，在院內曾無佩戴口罩，心臟停頓期間曾接受心肺復蘇。曾為其急救的護士及同層工作的管房，同樣驗出陽性。
detail_en: The patient had late-stage lung cancer, began staying at a private ward on 33/F, Hong Kong Sanatorium & Hospital, and had had coughs and phlegms. She was regularly visited by three of her family members. She developed fever on November 25 and breathing difficulties next day, and had a heart attack while awaiting the virus test result and passed away on November 26. She was later on diagnosed positive for the virus. She had a high viral load and weak immunity, requiring oxygen support and inhaled medications, and was sometimes without a mask. She was administered CPR during cardiac arrest by a nurse who, along with the housekeeper of the floor, tested positive for the virus too.
